app-bar\"`?** → `AppBar()`\n41\t3. **Has `data-flutter=\"bottom-nav\"`?** → `NavigationBar()`\n42\t4. **Has `data-flutter=\"hero\"`?** → `Hero(tag: ...)`\n43\t5. **Has `data-flutter=\"cached-image\"`?** → `CachedNetworkImage()`\n44\t6. **Is `<button>`?** → Determine button type from Tailwind classes\n45\t7. **Is `<img>`?** → `Image.network()` or `CachedNetworkImage()`\n46\t8. **Is text element (`<h1>`-`<h6>`, `<p>`, `<span>`)?** → `Text()`\n47\t9. **Has `flex flex-col`?** → `Column()`\n48\t10. **Has `flex` (default row)?** → `Row()`\n49\t11. **Has `grid`?** → `GridView()`\n50\t12. **Has `overflow-y-auto`?** → `SingleChildScrollView()`\n51\t13. **Has `overflow-x-auto`?** → `SingleChildScrollView(scrollDirection: Axis.horizontal)`\n52\t14. **Has `relative` with `absolute` children?** → `Stack()` + `Positioned()`\n53\t15. **Has `bg-*` + `rounded-*`?** → `DecoratedBox()` or `Container()`\n54\t16. **Has only `p-*`?** → `Padding()`\n55\t17. **Has only size classes?** → `SizedBox()`\n56\t\n57\t### Step 3: Extract Styling from Tailwind Classes\n58\t\n59\tFor each Tailwind class, look up the Flutter equivalent in `tailwind-to-flutter.md`:\n60\t\n61\t```html\n62\t<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n63\t```\n64\t\n65\tParses to:\n66\t- `flex flex-col` → `Column()`\n67\t- `gap-4` → 16px spacing between children\n68\t- `p-4` → `Padding(padding: EdgeInsets.all(16))`\n69\t- `bg-slate-900` → `color: Color(0xFF0F172A)`\n70\t- `rounded-xl` → `borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12)`\n71\t- `shadow-lg` → `boxShadow: [BoxShadow(...)]`\n72\t\n73\tResult:\n74\t```dart\n75\tContainer(\n76\t  padding: const EdgeInsets.all(16),\n77\t  decoration: BoxDecoration(\n78\t    color: const Color(0xFF0F172A),\n79\t    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12),\n80\t    boxShadow: const [\n81\t      BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 15, offset: Offset(0, 10)),\n82\t    ],\n83\t  ),\n84\t  child: Column(\n85\t    children: [\n86\t      child1,\n87\t      const SizedBox(height: 16),\n88\t      child2,\n89\t    ],\n90\t  ),\n91\t)\n92\t```\n93\t\n94\t### Step 4: Handle Text\n95\t\n96\t```html\n97\t<span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Novel Title</span>\n98\t```\n99\t\n100\t→ `fontSize: 18`, `fontWeight: FontWeight.w600`, `color: Colors.white`\n101\t\n102\t```dart\n103\tText(\n104\t  'Novel Title',\n105\t  style: TextStyle(fontSize: 18, fontWeight: FontWeight.w600, color: Colors.white),\n106\t)\n107\t```\n108\t\n109\t### Step 5: Handle Buttons\n110\t\n111\t| Tailwind Pattern | Flutter Button |\n112\t|---|---|\n113\t| Prominent `bg-{color}` + text color | `FilledButton` or `ElevatedButton` |\n114\t| `border` + no fill | `OutlinedButton` |\n115\t| Text only, no border/fill | `TextButton` |\n116\t| Icon only, circular | `IconButton` |\n117\t\n118\t### Step 6: Handle Images\n119\t\n120\t```html\n121\t<img class=\"w-20 h-28 rounded-lg object-cover\" src=\"...\" />\n122\t```\n123\t→ `ClipRRect` + `CachedNetworkImage(width: 80, height: 112, fit: BoxFit.cover)`\n124\t\n125\t### Step 7: Handle `data-flutter` Attributes\n126\t\n127\tOnly for Flutter-specific widgets with no HTML equivalent:\n128\t\n129\t| `data-flutter` | Flutter Widget | Extra Attributes |\n130\t|----------------|---------------|------------------|\n131\t| `scaffold` | `Scaffold()` | — |\n132\t| `app-bar` | `AppBar()` | — |\n133\t| `bottom-nav` | `NavigationBar()` | — |\n134\t| `nav-destination` | `NavigationDestination()` | `data-icon`, `data-label` |\n135\t| `fab` | `FloatingActionButton()` | `data-icon` |\n136\t| `hero` | `Hero()` | `data-tag` |\n137\t| `cached-image` | `CachedNetworkImage()` | — |\n138\t| `sliver-app-bar` | `SliverAppBar()` | `data-expanded-height`, `data-pinned` |\n139\t| `custom-scroll` | `CustomScrollView()` | — |\n140\t| `sliver-list` | `SliverList()` | — |\n141\t| `tab-bar` | `TabBar()` | — |\n142\t| `tab-view` | `TabBarView()` | — |\n143\t| `bottom-sheet` | `showModalBottomSheet()` | — |\n144\t| `safe-area` | `SafeArea()` | — |\n145\t| `refresh` | `RefreshIndicator()` | — |\n146\t\n147\t### Step 8: Generate Dart File\n148\t\n149\t```dart\n150\timport 'package:flutter/material.dart';\n151\timport 'package:cached_network_image/cached_network_image.dart';\n152\t\n153\tclass {WidgetName}Screen extends StatelessWidget {\n154\t  const {WidgetName}Screen({super.key});\n155\t\n156\t  @override\n157\t  Widget build(BuildContext context) {\n158\t    return Scaffold(\n159\t      // ... converted from Tailwind HTML\n160\t    );\n161\t  }\n162\t}\n163\t```\n164\t\n165\t### Step 9: Update Router & Verify\n166\t\n167\t1. Add route to `lib/router/app_router.dart`\n168\t2. `dart format lib/screens/{snake_id}/`\n169\t3. `dart analyze --no-fatal-infos lib/screens/{snake_id}/`\n170\t\n171\t---\n172\t\n173\t## Worked Example\n174\t\n175\t### Input (Tailwind HTML)\n176\t```html\n177\t<div data-flutter=\"scaffold\" class=\"flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-slate-950\">\n178\t  <header data-flutter=\"app-bar\" class=\"flex items-center h-14 px-2 bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-lg\">\n179\t    <button class=\"w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full\" aria-label=\"Back\">\n180\t      <svg><!-- arrow_back --></svg>\n181\t    </button>\n182\t    <h1 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white ml-3\">Home</h1>\n183\t  </header>\n184\t\n185\t  <main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto\">\n186\t    <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6 p-4\">\n187\t      <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Continue Reading</h2>\n188\t      <div class=\"bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-lg\">\n189\t        <div class=\"flex gap-3\">\n190\t          <img data-flutter=\"cached-image\" class=\"w-16 h-24 rounded-lg object-cover\"\n191\t               src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/n1/100/150\" />\n192\t          <div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 gap-1\">\n193\t            <span class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white\">The Dragon's Apprentice</span>\n194\t            <span class=\"text-sm text-slate-400\">Chapter 42 of 120</span>\n195\t            <div class=\"h-1.5 bg-slate-700 rounded-full mt-1\">\n196\t              <div class=\"h-full w-[35%] bg-amber-500 rounded-full\"></div>\n197\t            </div>\n198\t          </div>\n199\t        </div>\n200\t      </div>\n201\t    </div>\n202\t  </main>\n203\t\n204\t  <nav data-flutter=\"bottom-nav\" class=\"flex justify-around h-14 bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800\">\n205\t    <button data-flutter=\"nav-destination\" data-icon=\"home\" data-label=\"Home\"\n206\t            class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-amber-500\">\n207\t      <svg><!-- home --></svg><span class=\"text-xs\">Home</span>\n208\t    </button>\n209\t    <button data-flutter=\"nav-destination\" data-icon=\"search\" data-label=\"Browse\"\n210\t            class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-slate-500\">\n211\t      <svg><!-- search --></svg><span class=\"text-xs\">Browse</span>\n212\t    </button>\n213\t  </nav>\n214\t</div>\n215\t```\n216\t\n217\t### Output (Flutter)\n218\t```dart\n219\tScaffold(\n220\t  backgroundColor: const Color(0xFF020617),\n221\t  appBar: AppBar(\n222\t    backgroundColor: const Color(0xFF0F172A).withValues(alpha: 0.8),\n223\t    leading: IconButton(\n224\t      icon: const Icon(Icons.arrow_back), onPressed: () {}, tooltip: 'Back',\n225\t    ),\n226\t    title: const Text('Home',\n227\t      style: TextStyle(fontSize: 18, fontWeight: FontWeight.w600, color: Colors.white),\n228\t    ),\n229\t  ),\n230\t  body: SingleChildScrollView(\n231\t    child: Padding(\n232\t      padding: const EdgeInsets.all(16),\n233\t      child: Column(\n234\t        crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,\n235\t        children: [\n236\t          const Text('Continue Reading',\n237\t            style: TextStyle(fontSize: 20, fontWeight: FontWeight.w700, color: Colors.white),\n238\t          ),\n239\t          const SizedBox(height: 24),\n240\t          Container(\n241\t            padding: const EdgeInsets.all(16),\n242\t            decoration: BoxDecoration(\n243\t              color: const Color(0xFF1E293B),\n244\t              borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(16),\n245\t              boxShadow: const [BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 15, offset: Offset(0, 10))],\n246\t            ),\n247\t            child: Row(children: [\n248\t              ClipRRect(\n249\t                borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),\n250\t                child: CachedNetworkImage(\n251\t                  imageUrl: 'https://picsum.photos/seed/n1/100/150',\n252\t                  width: 64, height: 96, fit: BoxFit.cover,\n253\t                ),\n254\t              ),\n255\t              const SizedBox(width: 12),\n256\t              Expanded(child: Column(\n257\t                crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,\n258\t                children: [\n259\t                  const Text(\"The Dragon's Apprentice\",\n260\t                    style: TextStyle(fontSize: 16, fontWeight: FontWeight.w600, color: Colors.white)),\n261\t                  const SizedBox(height: 4),\n262\t                  const Text('Chapter 42 of 120',\n263\t                    style: TextStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Color(0xFF94A3B8))),\n264\t                  const SizedBox(height: 4),\n265\t                  ClipRRect(\n266\t                    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(9999),\n267\t                    child: const SizedBox(height: 6,\n268\t                      child: LinearProgressIndicator(value: 0.35,\n269\t                        backgroundColor: Color(0xFF334155),\n270\t                        valueColor: AlwaysStoppedAnimation(Color(0xFFF59E0B)))),\n271\t                  ),\n272\t                ],\n273\t              )),\n274\t            ]),\n275\t          ),\n276\t        ],\n277\t      ),\n278\t    ),\n279\t  ),\n280\t  bottomNavigationBar: NavigationBar(\n281\t    backgroundColor: const Color(0xFF0F172A),\n282\t    selectedIndex: 0,\n283\t    destinations: const [\n284\t      NavigationDestination(icon: Icon(Icons.home), label: 'Home'),\n285\t      NavigationDestination(icon: Icon(Icons.search), label: 'Browse'),\n286\t    ],\n287\t  ),\n288\t)\n289\t```\n290\t\n291\t---\n292\t\n293\t## Cross-Reference\n294\t\n295\t- **Tailwind → Flutter:** `references/tailwind-to-flutter.md` — complete class-by-class mapping\n296\t- **`data-flutter` hints:** `references/flutter-html-glossary.md` — Flutter-specific attributes\n297\t- **HTML generation:** `stitch-generate/SKILL.md` — how to produce Tailwind HTML\n298\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d694d667-118c-44d3-9ad5-314421a0ee8d","uuid":"047a9d25-9a8f-4c58-8a60-59c45e50320c","timestamp":"2026-05-18T23:46:16.480Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.converge/skills/stitch-flutter/SKILL.md","content":"# Stitch Flutter — Tailwind HTML → Pixel-Perfect Flutter\n\nConvert HTML + Tailwind CSS design mockups into production-ready Flutter widgets. AI produces beautiful Tailwind — this skill maps every utility class to its exact Flutter equivalent.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\n1. **AI generates Tailwind HTML** — what it's best at, highest design quality\n2. **Minimal `data-flutter` hints** — only for Flutter-specific widgets (Scaffold, AppBar, Hero, CachedImage) that have no HTML equivalent\n3. **Tailwind classes = Flutter styling** — every utility class maps to an exact Flutter property via `references/tailwind-to-flutter.md`\n4. **CSS is for browser preview** — the converter reads Tailwind classes + `data-flutter` attributes, not computed CSS\n\n## Inputs\n\n- `.stitch/designs/{screenId}/design.html` — Tailwind HTML mockup\n- `.stitch/system/DESIGN.md` — Design system specification\n\n## Output\n\n- `lib/screens/{snake_id}/{snake_id}_screen.dart` — Flutter screen widget\n\n---\n\n## Conversion Procedure\n\n### Step 1: Parse HTML Structure\n\nRead the HTML and identify:\n1. **`data-flutter` attributes** → Flutter-specific widgets (see glossary)\n2. **Tailwind classes on each element** → styling properties (see `tailwind-to-flutter.md`)\n3. **HTML element type** (`div`, `button`, `img`, `span`, `nav`, `header`) → widget type hints\n4. **Text content** → `Text()` widget strings\n5. **`aria-*` attributes** → `Semantics()` widgets\n6. **Inline SVG icons** → `Icon(Icons.{name})` or `SvgPicture.string()`\n\n### Step 2: Determine Widget Type\n\nFor each element, use this decision tree:\n\n1. **Has `data-flutter=\"scaffold\"`?** → `Scaffold()`\n2. **Has `data-flutter=\"app-bar\"`?** → `AppBar()`\n3. **Has `data-flutter=\"bottom-nav\"`?** → `NavigationBar()`\n4. **Has `data-flutter=\"hero\"`?** → `Hero(tag: ...)`\n5. **Has `data-flutter=\"cached-image\"`?** → `CachedNetworkImage()`\n6. **Is `<button>`?** → Determine button type from Tailwind classes\n7. **Is `<img>`?** → `Image.network()` or `CachedNetworkImage()`\n8. **Is text element (`<h1>`-`<h6>`, `<p>`, `<span>`)?** → `Text()`\n9. **Has `flex flex-col`?** → `Column()`\n10. **Has `flex` (default row)?** → `Row()`\n11. **Has `grid`?** → `GridView()`\n12. **Has `overflow-y-auto`?** → `SingleChildScrollView()`\n13. **Has `overflow-x-auto`?** → `SingleChildScrollView(scrollDirection: Axis.horizontal)`\n14. **Has `relative` with `absolute` children?** → `Stack()` + `Positioned()`\n15. **Has `bg-*` + `rounded-*`?** → `DecoratedBox()` or `Container()`\n16. **Has only `p-*`?** → `Padding()`\n17. **Has only size classes?** → `SizedBox()`\n\n### Step 3: Extract Styling from Tailwind Classes\n\nFor each Tailwind class, look up the Flutter equivalent in `tailwind-to-flutter.md`:\n\n```html\n<div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 p-4 bg-slate-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg\">\n```\n\nParses to:\n- `flex flex-col` → `Column()`\n- `gap-4` → 16px spacing between children\n- `p-4` → `Padding(padding: EdgeInsets.all(16))`\n- `bg-slate-900` → `color: Color(0xFF0F172A)`\n- `rounded-xl` → `borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12)`\n- `shadow-lg` → `boxShadow: [BoxShadow(...)]`\n\nResult:\n```dart\nContainer(\n  padding: const EdgeInsets.all(16),\n  decoration: BoxDecoration(\n    color: const Color(0xFF0F172A),\n    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12),\n    boxShadow: const [\n      BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 15, offset: Offset(0, 10)),\n    ],\n  ),\n  child: Column(\n    children: [\n      child1,\n      const SizedBox(height: 16),\n      child2,\n    ],\n  ),\n)\n```\n\n### Step 4: Handle Text\n\n```html\n<span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white\">Novel Title</span>\n```\n\n→ `fontSize: 18`, `fontWeight: FontWeight.w600`, `color: Colors.white`\n\n```dart\nText(\n  'Novel Title',\n  style: TextStyle(fontSize: 18, fontWeight: FontWeight.w600, color: Colors.white),\n)\n```\n\n### Step 5: Handle Buttons\n\n| Tailwind Pattern | Flutter Button |\n|---|---|\n| Prominent `bg-{color}` + text color | `FilledButton` or `ElevatedButton` |\n| `border` + no fill | `OutlinedButton` |\n| Text only, no border/fill | `TextButton` |\n| Icon only, circular | `IconButton` |\n\n### Step 6: Handle Images\n\n```html\n<img class=\"w-20 h-28 rounded-lg object-cover\" src=\"...\" />\n```\n→ `ClipRRect` + `CachedNetworkImage(width: 80, height: 112, fit: BoxFit.cover)`\n\n### Step 7: Handle `data-flutter` Attributes\n\nOnly for Flutter-specific widgets with no HTML equivalent:\n\n| `data-flutter` | Flutter Widget | Extra Attributes |\n|----------------|---------------|------------------|\n| `scaffold` | `Scaffold()` | — |\n| `app-bar` | `AppBar()` | — |\n| `bottom-nav` | `NavigationBar()` | — |\n| `nav-destination` | `NavigationDestination()` | `data-icon`, `data-label` |\n| `fab` | `FloatingActionButton()` | `data-icon` |\n| `hero` | `Hero()` | `data-tag` |\n| `cached-image` | `CachedNetworkImage()` | — |\n| `sliver-app-bar` | `SliverAppBar()` | `data-expanded-height`, `data-pinned` |\n| `custom-scroll` | `CustomScrollView()` | — |\n| `sliver-list` | `SliverList()` | — |\n| `tab-bar` | `TabBar()` | — |\n| `tab-view` | `TabBarView()` | — |\n| `bottom-sheet` | `showModalBottomSheet()` | — |\n| `safe-area` | `SafeArea()` | — |\n| `refresh` | `RefreshIndicator()` | — |\n\n### Step 8: Generate Dart File\n\n```dart\nimport 'package:flutter/material.dart';\nimport 'package:cached_network_image/cached_network_image.dart';\n\nclass {WidgetName}Screen extends StatelessWidget {\n  const {WidgetName}Screen({super.key});\n\n  @override\n  Widget build(BuildContext context) {\n    return Scaffold(\n      // ... converted from Tailwind HTML\n    );\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Step 9: Update Router & Verify\n\n1. Add route to `lib/router/app_router.dart`\n2. `dart format lib/screens/{snake_id}/`\n3. `dart analyze --no-fatal-infos lib/screens/{snake_id}/`\n\n---\n\n## Worked Example\n\n### Input (Tailwind HTML)\n```html\n<div data-flutter=\"scaffold\" class=\"flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-slate-950\">\n  <header data-flutter=\"app-bar\" class=\"flex items-center h-14 px-2 bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-lg\">\n    <button class=\"w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full\" aria-label=\"Back\">\n      <svg><!-- arrow_back --></svg>\n    </button>\n    <h1 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-white ml-3\">Home</h1>\n  </header>\n\n  <main class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto\">\n    <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6 p-4\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Continue Reading</h2>\n      <div class=\"bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-lg\">\n        <div class=\"flex gap-3\">\n          <img data-flutter=\"cached-image\" class=\"w-16 h-24 rounded-lg object-cover\"\n               src=\"https://picsum.photos/seed/n1/100/150\" />\n          <div class=\"flex flex-col flex-1 gap-1\">\n            <span class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white\">The Dragon's Apprentice</span>\n            <span class=\"text-sm text-slate-400\">Chapter 42 of 120</span>\n            <div class=\"h-1.5 bg-slate-700 rounded-full mt-1\">\n              <div class=\"h-full w-[35%] bg-amber-500 rounded-full\"></div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </main>\n\n  <nav data-flutter=\"bottom-nav\" class=\"flex justify-around h-14 bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-800\">\n    <button data-flutter=\"nav-destination\" data-icon=\"home\" data-label=\"Home\"\n            class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-amber-500\">\n      <svg><!-- home --></svg><span class=\"text-xs\">Home</span>\n    </button>\n    <button data-flutter=\"nav-destination\" data-icon=\"search\" data-label=\"Browse\"\n            class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 text-slate-500\">\n      <svg><!-- search --></svg><span class=\"text-xs\">Browse</span>\n    </button>\n  </nav>\n</div>\n```\n\n### Output (Flutter)\n```dart\nScaffold(\n  backgroundColor: const Color(0xFF020617),\n  appBar: AppBar(\n    backgroundColor: const Color(0xFF0F172A).withValues(alpha: 0.8),\n    leading: IconButton(\n      icon: const Icon(Icons.arrow_back), onPressed: () {}, tooltip: 'Back',\n    ),\n    title: const Text('Home',\n      style: TextStyle(fontSize: 18, fontWeight: FontWeight.w600, color: Colors.white),\n    ),\n  ),\n  body: SingleChildScrollView(\n    child: Padding(\n      padding: const EdgeInsets.all(16),\n      child: Column(\n        crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,\n        children: [\n          const Text('Continue Reading',\n            style: TextStyle(fontSize: 20, fontWeight: FontWeight.w700, color: Colors.white),\n          ),\n          const SizedBox(height: 24),\n          Container(\n            padding: const EdgeInsets.all(16),\n            decoration: BoxDecoration(\n              color: const Color(0xFF1E293B),\n              borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(16),\n              boxShadow: const [BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 15, offset: Offset(0, 10))],\n            ),\n            child: Row(children: [\n              ClipRRect(\n                borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(8),\n                child: CachedNetworkImage(\n                  imageUrl: 'https://picsum.photos/seed/n1/100/150',\n                  width: 64, height: 96, fit: BoxFit.cover,\n                ),\n              ),\n              const SizedBox(width: 12),\n              Expanded(child: Column(\n                crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,\n                children: [\n                  const Text(\"The Dragon's Apprentice\",\n                    style: TextStyle(fontSize: 16, fontWeight: FontWeight.w600, color: Colors.white)),\n                  const SizedBox(height: 4),\n                  const Text('Chapter 42 of 120',\n                    style: TextStyle(fontSize: 14, color: Color(0xFF94A3B8))),\n                  const SizedBox(height: 4),\n                  ClipRRect(\n                    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(9999),\n                    child: const SizedBox(height: 6,\n                      child: LinearProgressIndicator(value: 0.35,\n                        backgroundColor: Color(0xFF334155),\n                        valueColor: AlwaysStoppedAnimation(Color(0xFFF59E0B)))),\n                  ),\n                ],\n              )),\n            ]),\n          ),\n        ],\n      ),\n    ),\n  ),\n  bottomNavigationBar: NavigationBar(\n    backgroundColor: const Color(0xFF0F172A),\n    selectedIndex: 0,\n    destinations: const [\n      NavigationDestination(icon: Icon(Icons.home), label: 'Home'),\n      NavigationDestination(icon: Icon(Icons.search), label: 'Browse'),\n    ],\n  ),\n)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Cross-Reference\n\n- **Tailwind → Flutter:** `references/tailwind-to-flutter.md` — complete class-by-class mapping\n- **`data-flutter` hints:** `references/flutter-html-glossary.md` — Flutter-specific attributes\n- **HTML generation:** `stitch-generate/SKILL.md` — how to produce Tailwind HTML\n","numLines":298,"startLine":1,"totalLines":298}}}
