ustify-between` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween` |\n42\t| `justify-around` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceAround` |\n43\t| `justify-evenly` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly` |\n44\t\n45\t### Cross Axis Alignment\n46\t\n47\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n48\t|----------|---------|\n49\t| `items-start` | `CrossAxisAlignment.start` |\n50\t| `items-center` | `CrossAxisAlignment.center` |\n51\t| `items-end` | `CrossAxisAlignment.end` |\n52\t| `items-stretch` | `CrossAxisAlignment.stretch` |\n53\t| `items-baseline` | `CrossAxisAlignment.baseline` |\n54\t\n55\t### Self Alignment\n56\t\n57\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n58\t|----------|---------|\n59\t| `self-start` | `Align(alignment: Alignment.centerLeft)` |\n60\t| `self-center` | `Center()` |\n61\t| `self-end` | `Align(alignment: Alignment.centerRight)` |\n62\t| `self-stretch` | `SizedBox(width: double.infinity)` |\n63\t\n64\t### Gap (spacing between children)\n65\t\n66\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n67\t|----------|---------|\n68\t| `gap-0` | No spacing |\n69\t| `gap-0.5` | 2px SizedBox between children |\n70\t| `gap-1` | 4px |\n71\t| `gap-1.5` | 6px |\n72\t| `gap-2` | 8px |\n73\t| `gap-2.5` | 10px |\n74\t| `gap-3` | 12px |\n75\t| `gap-4` | 16px |\n76\t| `gap-5` | 20px |\n77\t| `gap-6` | 24px |\n78\t| `gap-8` | 32px |\n79\t| `gap-10` | 40px |\n80\t| `gap-12` | 48px |\n81\t| `gap-x-{n}` | Horizontal gap only (Row) |\n82\t| `gap-y-{n}` | Vertical gap only (Column) |\n83\t| `space-x-{n}` | SizedBox(width: {n*4}px) between Row children |\n84\t| `space-y-{n}` | SizedBox(height: {n*4}px) between Column children |\n85\t\n86\t**Implementation:** Insert `SizedBox(width/height: X)` between each child pair, or use Column/Row `spacing:` parameter (Flutter 3.27+).\n87\t\n88\t---\n89\t\n90\t## 3. Spacing Scale → Pixel Values\n91\t\n92\tAll spacing utilities (`p-`, `m-`, `gap-`, `w-`, `h-`, `inset-`, `top-`, etc.) use this scale:\n93\t\n94\t| Tailwind | Pixels | Tailwind | Pixels |\n95\t|----------|--------|----------|--------|\n96\t| `0` | 0 | `10` | 40 |