straints(maxWidth: 384))` |\n147\t| `max-w-md` | `maxWidth: 448` |\n148\t| `max-w-lg` | `maxWidth: 512` |\n149\t| `max-w-xl` | `maxWidth: 576` |\n150\t| `max-w-screen-sm` | `maxWidth: 640` |\n151\t| `size-{n}` | `SizedBox(width: {px}, height: {px})` |\n152\t| `aspect-square` | `AspectRatio(aspectRatio: 1)` |\n153\t| `aspect-video` | `AspectRatio(aspectRatio: 16/9)` |\n154\t\n155\t---\n156\t\n157\t## 6. Typography → TextStyle\n158\t\n159\t### Font Size\n160\t\n161\t| Tailwind | fontSize | lineHeight | Flutter TextTheme hint |\n162\t|----------|----------|------------|----------------------|\n163\t| `text-xs` | 12 | 16 | `labelSmall` |\n164\t| `text-sm` | 14 | 20 | `bodySmall` / `labelLarge` |\n165\t| `text-base` | 16 | 24 | `bodyLarge` |\n166\t| `text-lg` | 18 | 28 | `titleMedium` |\n167\t| `text-xl` | 20 | 28 | `titleLarge` |\n168\t| `text-2xl` | 24 | 32 | `headlineSmall` |\n169\t| `text-3xl` | 30 | 36 | `headlineMedium` |\n170\t| `text-4xl` | 36 | 40 | `headlineLarge` |\n171\t| `text-5xl` | 48 | 1.0 | `displaySmall` |\n172\t| `text-6xl` | 60 | 1.0 | `displayMedium` |\n173\t| `text-7xl` | 72 | 1.0 | `displayLarge` |\n174\t\n175\t### Font Weight\n176\t\n177\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n178\t|----------|---------|\n179\t| `font-thin` | `FontWeight.w100` |\n180\t| `font-extralight` | `FontWeight.w200` |\n181\t| `font-light` | `FontWeight.w300` |\n182\t| `font-normal` | `FontWeight.w400` |\n183\t| `font-medium` | `FontWeight.w500` |\n184\t| `font-semibold` | `FontWeight.w600` |\n185\t| `font-bold` | `FontWeight.w700` |\n186\t| `font-extrabold` | `FontWeight.w800` |\n187\t| `font-black` | `FontWeight.w900` |\n188\t\n189\t### Text Alignment\n190\t\n191\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n192\t|----------|---------|\n193\t| `text-left` | `TextAlign.left` |\n194\t| `text-center` | `TextAlign.center` |\n195\t| `text-right` | `TextAlign.right` |\n196\t| `text-justify` | `TextAlign.justify` |\n197\t\n198\t### Text Overflow\n199\t\n200\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n201\t|----------|---------|\n202\t| `truncate` | `overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis, maxLines: 1` |\n203\t| `text-ellipsis` | `overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis` |\n204\t| `text-clip` | `overflow: TextOverflow.clip` |\n205\t| `line-clamp-{n}` | `maxLines: n, overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis` |\n206\t\n207\t### Text Decoration\n208\t\n209\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n210\t|----------|---------|\n211\t| `underline` | `decoration: TextDecoration.underline` |\n212\t| `line-through` | `decoration: TextDecoration.lineThrough` |\n213\t| `no-underline` | `decoration: TextDecoration.none` |\n214\t| `italic` | `fontStyle: FontStyle.italic` |\n215\t| `not-italic` | `fontStyle: FontStyle.normal` |\n216\t| `uppercase` | Transform text to uppercase in Dart |\n217\t| `lowercase` | Transform text to lowercase in Dart |\n218\t| `capitalize` | Capitalize in Dart |\n219\t\n220\t### Letter & Line Spacing\n221\t\n222\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n223\t|----------|---------|\n224\t| `tracking-tighter` | `letterSpacing: -0.8` |\n225\t| `tracking-tight` | `letterSpacing: -0.4` |\n226\t| `tracking-normal` | `letterSpacing: 0` |\n227\t| `tracking-wide` | `letterSpacing: 0.4` |\n228\t| `tracking-wider` | `letterSpacing: 0.8` |\n229\t| `tracking-widest` | `letterSpacing: 1.6` |\n230\t| `leading-none` | `height: 1.0` (in TextStyle) |\n231\t| `leading-tight` | `height: 1.25` |\n232\t| `leading-snug` | `height: 1.375` |\n233\t| `leading-normal` | `height: 1.5` |\n234\t| `leading-relaxed` | `height: 1.625` |\n235\t| `leading-loose` | `height: 2.0` |\n236\t\n237\t---\n238\t\n239\t## 7. Colors → Color Values\n240\t\n241\t### Format\n242\tTailwind colors map to `Color(0xAARRGGBB)` in Flutter.\n243\t\n244\t`text-{color}` → `TextStyle(color: Color(...))`\n245\t`bg-{color}` → Container/DecoratedBox color or widget background\n246\t`border-{color}` → `BorderSide(color: Color(...))`\n247\t\n248\t### Opacity Modifier\n249\t`bg-black/50` → `Color(0xFF000000).withOpacity(0.5)` or `Colors.black.withValues(alpha: 0.5)`\n250\t\n251\t### Slate (most used dark palette)\n252\t\n253\t| Tailwind | Hex | Color() |\n254\t|----------|-----|---------|\n255\t| `slate-50` | #f8fafc | `Color(0xFFF8FAFC)` |\n256\t| `slate-100` | #f1f5f9 | `Color(0xFFF1F5F9)` |\n257\t| `slate-200` | #e2e8f0 | `Color(0xFFE2E8F0)` |\n258\t| `slate-300` | #cbd5e1 | `Color(0xFFCBD5E1)` |\n259\t| `slate-400` | #94a3b8 | `Color(0xFF94A3B8)` |\n260\t| `slate-500` | #64748b | `Color(0xFF64748B)` |\n261\t| `slate-600` | #475569 | `Color(0xFF475569)` |\n262\t| `slate-700` | #334155 | `Color(0xFF334155)` |\n263\t| `slate-800` | #1e293b | `Color(0xFF1E293B)` |\n264\t| `slate-900` | #0f172a | `Color(0xFF0F172A)` |\n265\t| `slate-950` | #020617 | `Color(0xFF020617)` |\n266\t\n267\t### Amber (warm accent)\n268\t\n269\t| Tailwind | Hex | Color() |\n270\t|----------|-----|---------|\n271\t| `amber-50` | #fffbeb | `Color(0xFFFFFBEB)` |\n272\t| `amber-100` | #fef3c7 | `Color(0xFFFEF3C7)` |\n273\t| `amber-200` | #fde68a | `Color(0xFFFDE68A)` |\n274\t| `amber-300` | #fcd34d | `Color(0xFFFCD34D)` |\n275\t| `amber-400` | #fbbf24 | `Color(0xFFFBBF24)` |\n276\t| `amber-500` | #f59e0b | `Color(0xFFF59E0B)` |\n277\t| `amber-600` | #d97706 | `Color(0xFFD97706)` |\n278\t| `amber-700` | #b45309 | `Color(0xFFB45309)` |\n279\t| `amber-800` | #92400e | `Color(0xFF92400E)` |\n280\t| `amber-900` | #78350f | `Color(0xFF78350F)` |\n281\t| `amber-950` | #451a03 | `Color(0xFF451A03)` |\n282\t\n283\t### Common Utility Colors\n284\t\n285\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n286\t|----------|---------|\n287\t| `white` | `Colors.white` |\n288\t| `black` | `Colors.black` |\n289\t| `transparent` | `Colors.transparent` |\n290\t| `current` | `(inherit from parent)` |\n291\t\n292\t### Full Palette Families\n293\t\n294\tThe following families follow the same 50-950 scale: `red`, `orange`, `yellow`, `lime`, `green`, `emerald`, `teal`, `cyan`, `sky`, `blue`, `indigo`, `violet`, `purple`, `fuchsia`, `pink`, `rose`, `stone`, `neutral`, `zinc`, `gray`.\n295\t\n296\tFor the full hex values, reference: https://tailwindcss.com/docs/customizing-colors\n297\t\n298\t**Conversion strategy:** Extract the hex value from the Tailwind color reference and use `Color(0xFF{hex})`.\n299\t\n300\t---\n301\t\n302\t## 8. Borders → Border / BorderSide\n303\t\n304\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n305\t|----------|---------|\n306\t| `border` | `Border.all(width: 1)` |\n307\t| `border-0` | No border |\n308\t| `border-2` | `Border.all(width: 2)` |\n309\t| `border-4` | `Border.all(width: 4)` |\n310\t| `border-t` | `Border(top: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n311\t| `border-b` | `Border(bottom: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n312\t| `border-l` | `Border(left: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n313\t| `border-r` | `Border(right: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n314\t| `border-{color}` | `BorderSide(color: Color(...))` |\n315\t| `border-dashed` | Custom `Paint` with dashed style |\n316\t| `divide-y` | `ListView.separated` with `Divider()` |\n317\t| `divide-x` | `VerticalDivider()` between items |\n318\t\n319\t---\n320\t\n321\t## 9. Border Radius → BorderRadius\n322\t\n323\t| Tailwind | Pixels | Flutter |\n324\t|----------|--------|---------|\n325\t| `rounded-none` | 0 | `BorderRadius.zero` |\n326\t| `rounded-sm` | 2 | `BorderRadius.circular(2)` |\n327\t| `rounded` | 4 | `BorderRadius.circular(4)` |\n328\t| `rounded-md` | 6 | `BorderRadius.circular(6)` |\n329\t| `rounded-lg` | 8 | `BorderRadius.circular(8)` |\n330\t| `rounded-xl` | 12 | `BorderRadius.circular(12)` |\n331\t| `rounded-2xl` | 16 | `BorderRadius.circular(16)` |\n332\t| `rounded-3xl` | 24 | `BorderRadius.circular(24)` |\n333\t| `rounded-full` | 9999 | `BorderRadius.circular(9999)` → pill/circle |\n334\t| `rounded-t-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.vertical(top: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n335\t| `rounded-b-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.vertical(bottom: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n336\t| `rounded-l-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.horizontal(left: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n337\t| `rounded-r-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.horizontal(right: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n338\t\n339\t**Wrapping:** Use `ClipRRect(borderRadius: ...)` for clipping, or `DecoratedBox`/`Container` for decoration.\n340\t\n341\t---\n342\t\n343\t## 10. Shadows → BoxShadow\n344\t\n345\t| Tailwind | Flutter BoxShadow |\n346\t|----------|-------------------|\n347\t| `shadow-sm` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 2, offset: Offset(0, 1))` |\n348\t| `shadow` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 3, offset: Offset(0, 1)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0F000000), blurRadius: 2, offset: Offset(0, 1))` |\n349\t| `shadow-md` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 6, offset: Offset(0, 4)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0F000000), blurRadius: 4, offset: Offset(0, 2))` |\n350\t| `shadow-lg` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 15, offset: Offset(0, 10)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 6, offset: Offset(0, 4))` |\n351\t| `shadow-xl` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 25, offset: Offset(0, 20)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 10, offset: Offset(0, 8))` |\n352\t| `shadow-2xl` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x40000000), blurRadius: 50, offset: Offset(0, 25))` |\n353\t| `shadow-none` | No shadow |\n354\t\n355\t---\n356\t\n357\t## 11. Overflow → Clip / Scroll\n358\t\n359\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n360\t|----------|---------|\n361\t| `overflow-hidden` | `clipBehavior: Clip.hardEdge` or `ClipRect`/`ClipRRect` |\n362\t| `overflow-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView()` |\n363\t| `overflow-scroll` | `SingleChildScrollView()` |\n364\t| `overflow-visible` | Default (no clip) |\n365\t| `overflow-x-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView(scrollDirection: Axis.horizontal)` |\n366\t| `overflow-y-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView(scrollDirection: Axis.vertical)` |\n367\t\n368\t---\n369\t\n370\t## 12. Opacity → Opacity Widget\n371\t\n372\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n373\t|----------|---------|\n374\t| `opacity-0` | `Opacity(opacity: 0)` |\n375\t| `opacity-5` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.05)` |\n376\t| `opacity-10` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.1)` |\n377\t| `opacity-25` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.25)` |\n378\t| `opacity-50` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.5)` |\n379\t| `opacity-75` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.75)` |\n380\t| `opacity-100` | (no wrapper needed) |\n381\t\n382\t---\n383\t\n384\t## 13. Position → Positioned\n385\t\n386\t| Tailwind | Flutter (inside Stack) |\n387\t|----------|---------|\n388\t| `absolute inset-0` | `Positioned.fill()` |\n389\t| `absolute top-0 left-0` | `Positioned(top: 0, left: 0)` |\n390\t| `absolute bottom-0 right-0` | `Positioned(bottom: 0, right: 0)` |\n391\t| `absolute top-{n}` | `Positioned(top: {px})` |\n392\t| `absolute bottom-{n}` | `Positioned(bottom: {px})` |\n393\t| `z-{n}` | Child order in Stack (later = higher) |\n394\t| `z-10` | Order index 10 |\n395\t\n396\t---\n397\t\n398\t## 14. Effects → Flutter Equivalents\n399\t\n400\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n401\t|----------|---------|\n402\t| `backdrop-blur-sm` | `BackdropFilter(filter: ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 4, sigmaY: 4))` |\n403\t| `backdrop-blur` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 8, sigmaY: 8)` |\n404\t| `backdrop-blur-md` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 12, sigmaY: 12)` |\n405\t| `backdrop-blur-lg` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 16, sigmaY: 16)` |\n406\t| `backdrop-blur-xl` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 24, sigmaY: 24)` |\n407\t| `bg-gradient-to-r` | `LinearGradient(begin: Alignment.centerLeft, end: Alignment.centerRight)` |\n408\t| `bg-gradient-to-b` | `LinearGradient(begin: Alignment.topCenter, end: Alignment.bottomCenter)` |\n409\t| `from-{color}` | First color in gradient stops |\n410\t| `via-{color}` | Middle color in gradient stops |\n411\t| `to-{color}` | Last color in gradient stops |\n412\t\n413\t---\n414\t\n415\t## 15. Transitions & Animations\n416\t\n417\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n418\t|----------|---------|\n419\t| `transition-all` | `AnimatedContainer(duration: Duration(milliseconds: 150))` |\n420\t| `transition-colors` | `AnimatedDefaultTextStyle` or `AnimatedContainer` |\n421\t| `duration-75` | `Duration(milliseconds: 75)` |\n422\t| `duration-100` | `Duration(milliseconds: 100)` |\n423\t| `duration-150` | `Duration(milliseconds: 150)` |\n424\t| `duration-200` | `Duration(milliseconds: 200)` |\n425\t| `duration-300` | `Duration(milliseconds: 300)` |\n426\t| `duration-500` | `Duration(milliseconds: 500)` |\n427\t| `duration-700` | `Duration(milliseconds: 700)` |\n428\t| `duration-1000` | `Duration(milliseconds: 1000)` |\n429\t| `ease-linear` | `Curves.linear` |\n430\t| `ease-in` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n431\t| `ease-out` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n432\t| `ease-in-out` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n433\t\n434\t---\n435\t\n436\t## 16. Image Fit → BoxFit\n437\t\n438\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n439\t|----------|---------|\n440\t| `object-contain` | `BoxFit.contain` |\n441\t| `object-cover` | `BoxFit.cover` |\n442\t| `object-fill` | `BoxFit.fill` |\n443\t| `object-none` | `BoxFit.none` |\n444\t| `object-scale-down` | `BoxFit.scaleDown` |\n445\t\n446\t---\n447\t\n448\t## 17. Cursor & Interaction\n449\t\n450\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n451\t|----------|---------|\n452\t| `cursor-pointer` | Wrap in `InkWell()` or `GestureDetector()` |\n453\t| `pointer-events-none` | `IgnorePointer()` |\n454\t| `select-none` | (default in Flutter) |\n455\t| `touch-manipulation` | (default in Flutter) |\n456\t\n457\t---\n458\t\n459\t## 18. Tailwind → Flutter Widget Decision Tree\n460\t\n461\tWhen converting a `<div>` with Tailwind classes:\n462\t\n463\t1. **Has `flex flex-col`?** → `Column()`\n464\t2. **Has `flex` or `flex flex-row`?** → `Row()`\n465\t3. **Has `grid`?** → `GridView()`\n466\t4. **Has `overflow-y-auto` or `overflow-auto`?** → `SingleChildScrollView()`\n467\t5. **Has `relative`?** → `Stack()` (its `absolute` children become `Positioned`)\n468\t6. **Has `bg-*` + `rounded-*` + `shadow-*`?** → `Container()` or `DecoratedBox()`\n469\t7. **Has only `p-*`?** → `Padding()`\n470\t8. **Has only `w-*` and/or `h-*`?** → `SizedBox()`\n471\t9. **Otherwise** → `Container()` or collapse into parent\n472\t\n473\tFor `<span>` / `<p>` / `<h1>-<h6>` with text classes → `Text()` with `TextStyle`\n474\t\n475\tFor `<button>` → Determine button type from styling:\n476\t- Has prominent background color → `FilledButton()` or `ElevatedButton()`\n477\t- Has border, no fill → `OutlinedButton()`\n478\t- Text only → `TextButton()`\n479\t- Icon only → `IconButton()`\n480\t\n481\tFor `<img>` → `CachedNetworkImage()` or `Image.asset()`\n482\t\n483\tFor `<svg>` → `Icon()` (Material) or `SvgPicture.string()`\n484\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d694d667-118c-44d3-9ad5-314421a0ee8d","uuid":"3df4a8bc-7a5e-475c-965a-69c407319c04","timestamp":"2026-05-18T23:46:21.088Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.converge/skills/stitch-flutter/references/tailwind-to-flutter.md","content":"# Tailwind CSS → Flutter Mapping\n\nComprehensive mapping of Tailwind utility classes to Flutter widget properties. The converter parses each Tailwind class and produces the exact Flutter equivalent.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Layout → Widget Type\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter Widget | Notes |\n|----------|---------------|-------|\n| `flex flex-col` | `Column()` | Vertical layout |\n| `flex` or `flex flex-row` | `Row()` | Horizontal layout (default axis) |\n| `inline-flex` | `Row(mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min)` | Inline row |\n| `grid grid-cols-{n}` | `GridView.count(crossAxisCount: n)` | Grid |\n| `block` | `SizedBox(width: double.infinity)` | Full width block |\n| `hidden` | `SizedBox.shrink()` or omit | Hidden element |\n| `relative` | `Stack()` (on parent) | Position context |\n| `absolute` | `Positioned()` | Absolute positioning inside Stack |\n| `fixed` | `Scaffold.bottomNavigationBar` or overlay | Fixed position |\n| `sticky` | `SliverAppBar(pinned: true)` | Sticky header |\n\n## 2. Flex Properties\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter | Notes |\n|----------|---------|-------|\n| `flex-1` | `Expanded(flex: 1)` | Fill remaining space |\n| `flex-auto` | `Expanded()` | Auto flex |\n| `flex-none` | (no wrapper) | Don't flex |\n| `flex-shrink-0` | (no wrapper) | Don't shrink |\n| `grow` | `Expanded()` | Grow to fill |\n| `flex-wrap` | `Wrap()` | Use Wrap instead of Row |\n| `flex-nowrap` | `Row()` | Default — no wrap |\n\n### Main Axis Alignment (Row → horizontal, Column → vertical)\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `justify-start` | `MainAxisAlignment.start` |\n| `justify-center` | `MainAxisAlignment.center` |\n| `justify-end` | `MainAxisAlignment.end` |\n| `justify-between` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween` |\n| `justify-around` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceAround` |\n| `justify-evenly` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly` |\n\n### Cross Axis Alignment\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `items-start` | `CrossAxisAlignment.start` |\n| `items-center` | `CrossAxisAlignment.center` |\n| `items-end` | `CrossAxisAlignment.end` |\n| `items-stretch` | `CrossAxisAlignment.stretch` |\n| `items-baseline` | `CrossAxisAlignment.baseline` |\n\n### Self Alignment\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `self-start` | `Align(alignment: Alignment.centerLeft)` |\n| `self-center` | `Center()` |\n| `self-end` | `Align(alignment: Alignment.centerRight)` |\n| `self-stretch` | `SizedBox(width: double.infinity)` |\n\n### Gap (spacing between children)\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `gap-0` | No spacing |\n| `gap-0.5` | 2px SizedBox between children |\n| `gap-1` | 4px |\n| `gap-1.5` | 6px |\n| `gap-2` | 8px |\n| `gap-2.5` | 10px |\n| `gap-3` | 12px |\n| `gap-4` | 16px |\n| `gap-5` | 20px |\n| `gap-6` | 24px |\n| `gap-8` | 32px |\n| `gap-10` | 40px |\n| `gap-12` | 48px |\n| `gap-x-{n}` | Horizontal gap only (Row) |\n| `gap-y-{n}` | Vertical gap only (Column) |\n| `space-x-{n}` | SizedBox(width: {n*4}px) between Row children |\n| `space-y-{n}` | SizedBox(height: {n*4}px) between Column children |\n\n**Implementation:** Insert `SizedBox(width/height: X)` between each child pair, or use Column/Row `spacing:` parameter (Flutter 3.27+).\n\n---\n\n## 3. Spacing Scale → Pixel Values\n\nAll spacing utilities (`p-`, `m-`, `gap-`, `w-`, `h-`, `inset-`, `top-`, etc.) use this scale:\n\n| Tailwind | Pixels | Tailwind | Pixels |\n|----------|--------|----------|--------|\n| `0` | 0 | `10` | 40 |\n| `px` | 1 | `11` | 44 |\n| `0.5` | 2 | `12` | 48 |\n| `1` | 4 | `14` | 56 |\n| `1.5` | 6 | `16` | 64 |\n| `2` | 8 | `20` | 80 |\n| `2.5` | 10 | `24` | 96 |\n| `3` | 12 | `28` | 112 |\n| `3.5` | 14 | `32` | 128 |\n| `4` | 16 | `36` | 144 |\n| `5` | 20 | `40` | 160 |\n| `6` | 24 | `44` | 176 |\n| `7` | 28 | `48` | 192 |\n| `8` | 32 | `52` | 208 |\n| `9` | 36 | `56` | 224 |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Padding → EdgeInsets\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `p-{n}` | `Padding(padding: EdgeInsets.all({px}))` |\n| `px-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: {px})` |\n| `py-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: {px})` |\n| `pt-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(top: {px})` |\n| `pb-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(bottom: {px})` |\n| `pl-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(left: {px})` |\n| `pr-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(right: {px})` |\n| `ps-{n}` | `EdgeInsetsDirectional.only(start: {px})` |\n| `pe-{n}` | `EdgeInsetsDirectional.only(end: {px})` |\n\n**Combined:** `px-4 py-2` → `EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 16, vertical: 8)`\n\n**Wrapping:** Use `Padding()` widget wrapping the child.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Width & Height → SizedBox / Constraints\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `w-{n}` | `SizedBox(width: {px})` or `width: {px}` in Container |\n| `h-{n}` | `SizedBox(height: {px})` or `height: {px}` in Container |\n| `w-full` | `SizedBox(width: double.infinity)` |\n| `h-full` | `SizedBox(height: double.infinity)` |\n| `w-screen` | `MediaQuery.of(context).size.width` |\n| `h-screen` | `MediaQuery.of(context).size.height` |\n| `min-w-0` | `ConstrainedBox(constraints: BoxConstraints(minWidth: 0))` |\n| `min-h-screen` | `ConstrainedBox(constraints: BoxConstraints(minHeight: screenHeight))` |\n| `max-w-sm` | `ConstrainedBox(constraints: BoxConstraints(maxWidth: 384))` |\n| `max-w-md` | `maxWidth: 448` |\n| `max-w-lg` | `maxWidth: 512` |\n| `max-w-xl` | `maxWidth: 576` |\n| `max-w-screen-sm` | `maxWidth: 640` |\n| `size-{n}` | `SizedBox(width: {px}, height: {px})` |\n| `aspect-square` | `AspectRatio(aspectRatio: 1)` |\n| `aspect-video` | `AspectRatio(aspectRatio: 16/9)` |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Typography → TextStyle\n\n### Font Size\n\n| Tailwind | fontSize | lineHeight | Flutter TextTheme hint |\n|----------|----------|------------|----------------------|\n| `text-xs` | 12 | 16 | `labelSmall` |\n| `text-sm` | 14 | 20 | `bodySmall` / `labelLarge` |\n| `text-base` | 16 | 24 | `bodyLarge` |\n| `text-lg` | 18 | 28 | `titleMedium` |\n| `text-xl` | 20 | 28 | `titleLarge` |\n| `text-2xl` | 24 | 32 | `headlineSmall` |\n| `text-3xl` | 30 | 36 | `headlineMedium` |\n| `text-4xl` | 36 | 40 | `headlineLarge` |\n| `text-5xl` | 48 | 1.0 | `displaySmall` |\n| `text-6xl` | 60 | 1.0 | `displayMedium` |\n| `text-7xl` | 72 | 1.0 | `displayLarge` |\n\n### Font Weight\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `font-thin` | `FontWeight.w100` |\n| `font-extralight` | `FontWeight.w200` |\n| `font-light` | `FontWeight.w300` |\n| `font-normal` | `FontWeight.w400` |\n| `font-medium` | `FontWeight.w500` |\n| `font-semibold` | `FontWeight.w600` |\n| `font-bold` | `FontWeight.w700` |\n| `font-extrabold` | `FontWeight.w800` |\n| `font-black` | `FontWeight.w900` |\n\n### Text Alignment\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `text-left` | `TextAlign.left` |\n| `text-center` | `TextAlign.center` |\n| `text-right` | `TextAlign.right` |\n| `text-justify` | `TextAlign.justify` |\n\n### Text Overflow\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `truncate` | `overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis, maxLines: 1` |\n| `text-ellipsis` | `overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis` |\n| `text-clip` | `overflow: TextOverflow.clip` |\n| `line-clamp-{n}` | `maxLines: n, overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis` |\n\n### Text Decoration\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `underline` | `decoration: TextDecoration.underline` |\n| `line-through` | `decoration: TextDecoration.lineThrough` |\n| `no-underline` | `decoration: TextDecoration.none` |\n| `italic` | `fontStyle: FontStyle.italic` |\n| `not-italic` | `fontStyle: FontStyle.normal` |\n| `uppercase` | Transform text to uppercase in Dart |\n| `lowercase` | Transform text to lowercase in Dart |\n| `capitalize` | Capitalize in Dart |\n\n### Letter & Line Spacing\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `tracking-tighter` | `letterSpacing: -0.8` |\n| `tracking-tight` | `letterSpacing: -0.4` |\n| `tracking-normal` | `letterSpacing: 0` |\n| `tracking-wide` | `letterSpacing: 0.4` |\n| `tracking-wider` | `letterSpacing: 0.8` |\n| `tracking-widest` | `letterSpacing: 1.6` |\n| `leading-none` | `height: 1.0` (in TextStyle) |\n| `leading-tight` | `height: 1.25` |\n| `leading-snug` | `height: 1.375` |\n| `leading-normal` | `height: 1.5` |\n| `leading-relaxed` | `height: 1.625` |\n| `leading-loose` | `height: 2.0` |\n\n---\n\n## 7. Colors → Color Values\n\n### Format\nTailwind colors map to `Color(0xAARRGGBB)` in Flutter.\n\n`text-{color}` → `TextStyle(color: Color(...))`\n`bg-{color}` → Container/DecoratedBox color or widget background\n`border-{color}` → `BorderSide(color: Color(...))`\n\n### Opacity Modifier\n`bg-black/50` → `Color(0xFF000000).withOpacity(0.5)` or `Colors.black.withValues(alpha: 0.5)`\n\n### Slate (most used dark palette)\n\n| Tailwind | Hex | Color() |\n|----------|-----|---------|\n| `slate-50` | #f8fafc | `Color(0xFFF8FAFC)` |\n| `slate-100` | #f1f5f9 | `Color(0xFFF1F5F9)` |\n| `slate-200` | #e2e8f0 | `Color(0xFFE2E8F0)` |\n| `slate-300` | #cbd5e1 | `Color(0xFFCBD5E1)` |\n| `slate-400` | #94a3b8 | `Color(0xFF94A3B8)` |\n| `slate-500` | #64748b | `Color(0xFF64748B)` |\n| `slate-600` | #475569 | `Color(0xFF475569)` |\n| `slate-700` | #334155 | `Color(0xFF334155)` |\n| `slate-800` | #1e293b | `Color(0xFF1E293B)` |\n| `slate-900` | #0f172a | `Color(0xFF0F172A)` |\n| `slate-950` | #020617 | `Color(0xFF020617)` |\n\n### Amber (warm accent)\n\n| Tailwind | Hex | Color() |\n|----------|-----|---------|\n| `amber-50` | #fffbeb | `Color(0xFFFFFBEB)` |\n| `amber-100` | #fef3c7 | `Color(0xFFFEF3C7)` |\n| `amber-200` | #fde68a | `Color(0xFFFDE68A)` |\n| `amber-300` | #fcd34d | `Color(0xFFFCD34D)` |\n| `amber-400` | #fbbf24 | `Color(0xFFFBBF24)` |\n| `amber-500` | #f59e0b | `Color(0xFFF59E0B)` |\n| `amber-600` | #d97706 | `Color(0xFFD97706)` |\n| `amber-700` | #b45309 | `Color(0xFFB45309)` |\n| `amber-800` | #92400e | `Color(0xFF92400E)` |\n| `amber-900` | #78350f | `Color(0xFF78350F)` |\n| `amber-950` | #451a03 | `Color(0xFF451A03)` |\n\n### Common Utility Colors\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `white` | `Colors.white` |\n| `black` | `Colors.black` |\n| `transparent` | `Colors.transparent` |\n| `current` | `(inherit from parent)` |\n\n### Full Palette Families\n\nThe following families follow the same 50-950 scale: `red`, `orange`, `yellow`, `lime`, `green`, `emerald`, `teal`, `cyan`, `sky`, `blue`, `indigo`, `violet`, `purple`, `fuchsia`, `pink`, `rose`, `stone`, `neutral`, `zinc`, `gray`.\n\nFor the full hex values, reference: https://tailwindcss.com/docs/customizing-colors\n\n**Conversion strategy:** Extract the hex value from the Tailwind color reference and use `Color(0xFF{hex})`.\n\n---\n\n## 8. Borders → Border / BorderSide\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `border` | `Border.all(width: 1)` |\n| `border-0` | No border |\n| `border-2` | `Border.all(width: 2)` |\n| `border-4` | `Border.all(width: 4)` |\n| `border-t` | `Border(top: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n| `border-b` | `Border(bottom: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n| `border-l` | `Border(left: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n| `border-r` | `Border(right: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n| `border-{color}` | `BorderSide(color: Color(...))` |\n| `border-dashed` | Custom `Paint` with dashed style |\n| `divide-y` | `ListView.separated` with `Divider()` |\n| `divide-x` | `VerticalDivider()` between items |\n\n---\n\n## 9. Border Radius → BorderRadius\n\n| Tailwind | Pixels | Flutter |\n|----------|--------|---------|\n| `rounded-none` | 0 | `BorderRadius.zero` |\n| `rounded-sm` | 2 | `BorderRadius.circular(2)` |\n| `rounded` | 4 | `BorderRadius.circular(4)` |\n| `rounded-md` | 6 | `BorderRadius.circular(6)` |\n| `rounded-lg` | 8 | `BorderRadius.circular(8)` |\n| `rounded-xl` | 12 | `BorderRadius.circular(12)` |\n| `rounded-2xl` | 16 | `BorderRadius.circular(16)` |\n| `rounded-3xl` | 24 | `BorderRadius.circular(24)` |\n| `rounded-full` | 9999 | `BorderRadius.circular(9999)` → pill/circle |\n| `rounded-t-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.vertical(top: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n| `rounded-b-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.vertical(bottom: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n| `rounded-l-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.horizontal(left: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n| `rounded-r-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.horizontal(right: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n\n**Wrapping:** Use `ClipRRect(borderRadius: ...)` for clipping, or `DecoratedBox`/`Container` for decoration.\n\n---\n\n## 10. Shadows → BoxShadow\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter BoxShadow |\n|----------|-------------------|\n| `shadow-sm` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 2, offset: Offset(0, 1))` |\n| `shadow` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 3, offset: Offset(0, 1)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0F000000), blurRadius: 2, offset: Offset(0, 1))` |\n| `shadow-md` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 6, offset: Offset(0, 4)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0F000000), blurRadius: 4, offset: Offset(0, 2))` |\n| `shadow-lg` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 15, offset: Offset(0, 10)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 6, offset: Offset(0, 4))` |\n| `shadow-xl` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 25, offset: Offset(0, 20)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 10, offset: Offset(0, 8))` |\n| `shadow-2xl` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x40000000), blurRadius: 50, offset: Offset(0, 25))` |\n| `shadow-none` | No shadow |\n\n---\n\n## 11. Overflow → Clip / Scroll\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `overflow-hidden` | `clipBehavior: Clip.hardEdge` or `ClipRect`/`ClipRRect` |\n| `overflow-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView()` |\n| `overflow-scroll` | `SingleChildScrollView()` |\n| `overflow-visible` | Default (no clip) |\n| `overflow-x-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView(scrollDirection: Axis.horizontal)` |\n| `overflow-y-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView(scrollDirection: Axis.vertical)` |\n\n---\n\n## 12. Opacity → Opacity Widget\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `opacity-0` | `Opacity(opacity: 0)` |\n| `opacity-5` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.05)` |\n| `opacity-10` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.1)` |\n| `opacity-25` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.25)` |\n| `opacity-50` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.5)` |\n| `opacity-75` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.75)` |\n| `opacity-100` | (no wrapper needed) |\n\n---\n\n## 13. Position → Positioned\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter (inside Stack) |\n|----------|---------|\n| `absolute inset-0` | `Positioned.fill()` |\n| `absolute top-0 left-0` | `Positioned(top: 0, left: 0)` |\n| `absolute bottom-0 right-0` | `Positioned(bottom: 0, right: 0)` |\n| `absolute top-{n}` | `Positioned(top: {px})` |\n| `absolute bottom-{n}` | `Positioned(bottom: {px})` |\n| `z-{n}` | Child order in Stack (later = higher) |\n| `z-10` | Order index 10 |\n\n---\n\n## 14. Effects → Flutter Equivalents\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `backdrop-blur-sm` | `BackdropFilter(filter: ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 4, sigmaY: 4))` |\n| `backdrop-blur` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 8, sigmaY: 8)` |\n| `backdrop-blur-md` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 12, sigmaY: 12)` |\n| `backdrop-blur-lg` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 16, sigmaY: 16)` |\n| `backdrop-blur-xl` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 24, sigmaY: 24)` |\n| `bg-gradient-to-r` | `LinearGradient(begin: Alignment.centerLeft, end: Alignment.centerRight)` |\n| `bg-gradient-to-b` | `LinearGradient(begin: Alignment.topCenter, end: Alignment.bottomCenter)` |\n| `from-{color}` | First color in gradient stops |\n| `via-{color}` | Middle color in gradient stops |\n| `to-{color}` | Last color in gradient stops |\n\n---\n\n## 15. Transitions & Animations\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `transition-all` | `AnimatedContainer(duration: Duration(milliseconds: 150))` |\n| `transition-colors` | `AnimatedDefaultTextStyle` or `AnimatedContainer` |\n| `duration-75` | `Duration(milliseconds: 75)` |\n| `duration-100` | `Duration(milliseconds: 100)` |\n| `duration-150` | `Duration(milliseconds: 150)` |\n| `duration-200` | `Duration(milliseconds: 200)` |\n| `duration-300` | `Duration(milliseconds: 300)` |\n| `duration-500` | `Duration(milliseconds: 500)` |\n| `duration-700` | `Duration(milliseconds: 700)` |\n| `duration-1000` | `Duration(milliseconds: 1000)` |\n| `ease-linear` | `Curves.linear` |\n| `ease-in` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n| `ease-out` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| `ease-in-out` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n\n---\n\n## 16. Image Fit → BoxFit\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `object-contain` | `BoxFit.contain` |\n| `object-cover` | `BoxFit.cover` |\n| `object-fill` | `BoxFit.fill` |\n| `object-none` | `BoxFit.none` |\n| `object-scale-down` | `BoxFit.scaleDown` |\n\n---\n\n## 17. Cursor & Interaction\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `cursor-pointer` | Wrap in `InkWell()` or `GestureDetector()` |\n| `pointer-events-none` | `IgnorePointer()` |\n| `select-none` | (default in Flutter) |\n| `touch-manipulation` | (default in Flutter) |\n\n---\n\n## 18. Tailwind → Flutter Widget Decision Tree\n\nWhen converting a `<div>` with Tailwind classes:\n\n1. **Has `flex flex-col`?** → `Column()`\n2. **Has `flex` or `flex flex-row`?** → `Row()`\n3. **Has `grid`?** → `GridView()`\n4. **Has `overflow-y-auto` or `overflow-auto`?** → `SingleChildScrollView()`\n5. **Has `relative`?** → `Stack()` (its `absolute` children become `Positioned`)\n6. **Has `bg-*` + `rounded-*` + `shadow-*`?** → `Container()` or `DecoratedBox()`\n7. **Has only `p-*`?** → `Padding()`\n8. **Has only `w-*` and/or `h-*`?** → `SizedBox()`\n9. **Otherwise** → `Container()` or collapse into parent\n\nFor `<span>` / `<p>` / `<h1>-<h6>` with text classes → `Text()` with `TextStyle`\n\nFor `<button>` → Determine button type from styling:\n- Has prominent background color → `FilledButton()` or `ElevatedButton()`\n- Has border, no fill → `OutlinedButton()`\n- Text only → `TextButton()`\n- Icon only → `IconButton()`\n\nFor `<img>` → `CachedNetworkImage()` or `Image.asset()`\n\nFor `<svg>` → `Icon()` (Material) or `SvgPicture.string()`\n","numLines":484,"startLine":1,"totalLines":484}}}
[2026-05-18T23:46:21.090Z] [STREAM_EVENT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_5yncl9xok4i6_3","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Tailwind CSS → Flutter Mapping\n2\t\n3\tComprehensive mapping of Tailwind utility classes to Flutter widget properties. The converter parses each Tailwind class and produces the exact Flutter equivalent.\n4\t\n5\t---\n6\t\n7\t## 1. Layout → Widget Type\n8\t\n9\t| Tailwind | Flutter Widget | Notes |\n10\t|----------|---------------|-------|\n11\t| `flex flex-col` | `Column()` | Vertical layout |\n12\t| `flex` or `flex flex-row` | `Row()` | Horizontal layout (default axis) |\n13\t| `inline-flex` | `Row(mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min)` | Inline row |\n14\t| `grid grid-cols-{n}` | `GridView.count(crossAxisCount: n)` | Grid |\n15\t| `block` | `SizedBox(width: double.infinity)` | Full width block |\n16\t| `hidden` | `SizedBox.shrink()` or omit | Hidden element |\n17\t| `relative` | `Stack()` (on parent) | Position context |\n18\t| `absolute` | `Positioned()` | Absolute positioning inside Stack |\n19\t| `fixed` | `Scaffold.bottomNavigationBar` or overlay | Fixed position |\n20\t| `sticky` | `SliverAppBar(pinned: true)` | Sticky header |\n21\t\n22\t## 2. Flex Properties\n23\t\n24\t| Tailwind | Flutter | Notes |\n25\t|----------|---------|-------|\n26\t| `flex-1` | `Expanded(flex: 1)` | Fill remaining space |\n27\t| `flex-auto` | `Expanded()` | Auto flex |\n28\t| `flex-none` | (no wrapper) | Don't flex |\n29\t| `flex-shrink-0` | (no wrapper) | Don't shrink |\n30\t| `grow` | `Expanded()` | Grow to fill |\n31\t| `flex-wrap` | `Wrap()` | Use Wrap instead of Row |\n32\t| `flex-nowrap` | `Row()` | Default — no wrap |\n33\t\n34\t### Main Axis Alignment (Row → horizontal, Column → vertical)\n35\t\n36\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n37\t|----------|---------|\n38\t| `justify-start` | `MainAxisAlignment.start` |\n39\t| `justify-center` | `MainAxisAlignment.center` |\n40\t| `justify-end` | `MainAxisAlignment.end` |\n41\t| `justify-between` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween` |\n42\t| `justify-around` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceAround` |\n43\t| `justify-evenly` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly` |\n44\t\n45\t### Cross Axis Alignment\n46\t\n47\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n48\t|----------|---------|\n49\t| `items-start` | `CrossAxisAlignment.start` |\n50\t| `items-center` | `CrossAxisAlignment.center` |\n51\t| `items-end` | `CrossAxisAlignment.end` |\n52\t| `items-stretch` | `CrossAxisAlignment.stretch` |\n53\t| `items-baseline` | `CrossAxisAlignment.baseline` |\n54\t\n55\t### Self Alignment\n56\t\n57\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n58\t|----------|---------|\n59\t| `self-start` | `Align(alignment: Alignment.centerLeft)` |\n60\t| `self-center` | `Center()` |\n61\t| `self-end` | `Align(alignment: Alignment.centerRight)` |\n62\t| `self-stretch` | `SizedBox(width: double.infinity)` |\n63\t\n64\t### Gap (spacing between children)\n65\t\n66\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n67\t|----------|---------|\n68\t| `gap-0` | No spacing |\n69\t| `gap-0.5` | 2px SizedBox between children |\n70\t| `gap-1` | 4px |\n71\t| `gap-1.5` | 6px |\n72\t| `gap-2` | 8px |\n73\t| `gap-2.5` | 10px |\n74\t| `gap-3` | 12px |\n75\t| `gap-4` | 16px |\n76\t| `gap-5` | 20px |\n77\t| `gap-6` | 24px |\n78\t| `gap-8` | 32px |\n79\t| `gap-10` | 40px |\n80\t| `gap-12` | 48px |\n81\t| `gap-x-{n}` | Horizontal gap only (Row) |\n82\t| `gap-y-{n}` | Vertical gap only (Column) |\n83\t| `space-x-{n}` | SizedBox(width: {n*4}px) between Row children |\n84\t| `space-y-{n}` | SizedBox(height: {n*4}px) between Column children |\n85\t\n86\t**Implementation:** Insert `SizedBox(width/height: X)` between each child pair, or use Column/Row `spacing:` parameter (Flutter 3.27+).\n87\t\n88\t---\n89\t\n90\t## 3. Spacing Scale → Pixel Values\n91\t\n92\tAll spacing utilities (`p-`, `m-`, `gap-`, `w-`, `h-`, `inset-`, `top-`, etc.) use this scale:\n93\t\n94\t| Tailwind | Pixels | Tailwind | Pixels |\n95\t|----------|--------|----------|--------|\n96\t| `0` | 0 | `10` | 40 |\n97\t| `px` | 1 | `11` | 44 |\n98\t| `0.5` | 2 | `12` | 48 |\n99\t| `1` | 4 | `14` | 56 |\n100\t| `1.5` | 6 | `16` | 64 |\n101\t| `2` | 8 | `20` | 80 |\n102\t| `2.5` | 10 | `24` | 96 |\n103\t| `3` | 12 | `28` | 112 |\n104\t| `3.5` | 14 | `32` | 128 |\n105\t| `4` | 16 | `36` | 144 |\n106\t| `5` | 20 | `40` | 160 |\n107\t| `6` | 24 | `44` | 176 |\n108\t| `7` | 28 | `48` | 192 |\n109\t| `8` | 32 | `52` | 208 |\n110\t| `9` | 36 | `56` | 224 |\n111\t\n112\t---\n113\t\n114\t## 4. Padding → EdgeInsets\n115\t\n116\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n117\t|----------|---------|\n118\t| `p-{n}` | `Padding(padding: EdgeInsets.all({px}))` |\n119\t| `px-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: {px})` |\n120\t| `py-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: {px})` |\n121\t| `pt-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(top: {px})` |\n122\t| `pb-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(bottom: {px})` |\n123\t| `pl-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(left: {px})` |\n124\t| `pr-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(right: {px})` |\n125\t| `ps-{n}` | `EdgeInsetsDirectional.only(start: {px})` |\n126\t| `pe-{n}` | `EdgeInsetsDirectional.only(end: {px})` |\n127\t\n128\t**Combined:** `px-4 py-2` → `EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 16, vertical: 8)`\n129\t\n130\t**Wrapping:** Use `Padding()` widget wrapping the child.\n131\t\n132\t---\n133\t\n134\t## 5. Width & Height → SizedBox / Constraints\n135\t\n136\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n137\t|----------|---------|\n138\t| `w-{n}` | `SizedBox(width: {px})` or `width: {px}` in Container |\n139\t| `h-{n}` | `SizedBox(height: {px})` or `height: {px}` in Container |\n140\t| `w-full` | `SizedBox(width: double.infinity)` |\n141\t| `h-full` | `SizedBox(height: double.infinity)` |\n142\t| `w-screen` | `MediaQuery.of(context).size.width` |\n143\t| `h-screen` | `MediaQuery.of(context).size.height` |\n144\t| `min-w-0` | `ConstrainedBox(constraints: BoxConstraints(minWidth: 0))` |\n145\t| `min-h-screen` | `ConstrainedBox(constraints: BoxConstraints(minHeight: screenHeight))` |\n146\t| `max-w-sm` | `ConstrainedBox(constraints: BoxConstraints(maxWidth: 384))` |\n147\t| `max-w-md` | `maxWidth: 448` |\n148\t| `max-w-lg` | `maxWidth: 512` |\n149\t| `max-w-xl` | `maxWidth: 576` |\n150\t| `max-w-screen-sm` | `maxWidth: 640` |\n151\t| `size-{n}` | `SizedBox(width: {px}, height: {px})` |\n152\t| `aspect-square` | `AspectRatio(aspectRatio: 1)` |\n153\t| `aspect-video` | `AspectRatio(aspectRatio: 16/9)` |\n154\t\n155\t---\n156\t\n157\t## 6. Typography → TextStyle\n158\t\n159\t### Font Size\n160\t\n161\t| Tailwind | fontSize | lineHeight | Flutter TextTheme hint |\n162\t|----------|----------|------------|----------------------|\n163\t| `text-xs` | 12 | 16 | `labelSmall` |\n164\t| `text-sm` | 14 | 20 | `bodySmall` / `labelLarge` |\n165\t| `text-base` | 16 | 24 | `bodyLarge` |\n166\t| `text-lg` | 18 | 28 | `titleMedium` |\n167\t| `text-xl` | 20 | 28 | `titleLarge` |\n168\t| `text-2xl` | 24 | 32 | `headlineSmall` |\n169\t| `text-3xl` | 30 | 36 | `headlineMedium` |\n170\t| `text-4xl` | 36 | 40 | `headlineLarge` |\n171\t| `text-5xl` | 48 | 1.0 | `displaySmall` |\n172\t| `text-6xl` | 60 | 1.0 | `displayMedium` |\n173\t| `text-7xl` | 72 | 1.0 | `displayLarge` |\n174\t\n175\t### Font Weight\n176\t\n177\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n178\t|----------|---------|\n179\t| `font-thin` | `FontWeight.w100` |\n180\t| `font-extralight` | `FontWeight.w200` |\n181\t| `font-light` | `FontWeight.w300` |\n182\t| `font-normal` | `FontWeight.w400` |\n183\t| `font-medium` | `FontWeight.w500` |\n184\t| `font-semibold` | `FontWeight.w600` |\n185\t| `font-bold` | `FontWeight.w700` |\n186\t| `font-extrabold` | `FontWeight.w800` |\n187\t| `font-black` | `FontWeight.w900` |\n188\t\n189\t### Text Alignment\n190\t\n191\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n192\t|----------|---------|\n193\t| `text-left` | `TextAlign.left` |\n194\t| `text-center` | `TextAlign.center` |\n195\t| `text-right` | `TextAlign.right` |\n196\t| `text-justify` | `TextAlign.justify` |\n197\t\n198\t### Text Overflow\n199\t\n200\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n201\t|----------|---------|\n202\t| `truncate` | `overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis, maxLines: 1` |\n203\t| `text-ellipsis` | `overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis` |\n204\t| `text-clip` | `overflow: TextOverflow.clip` |\n205\t| `line-clamp-{n}` | `maxLines: n, overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis` |\n206\t\n207\t### Text Decoration\n208\t\n209\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n210\t|----------|---------|\n211\t| `underline` | `decoration: TextDecoration.underline` |\n212\t| `line-through` | `decoration: TextDecoration.lineThrough` |\n213\t| `no-underline` | `decoration: TextDecoration.none` |\n214\t| `italic` | `fontStyle: FontStyle.italic` |\n215\t| `not-italic` | `fontStyle: FontStyle.normal` |\n216\t| `uppercase` | Transform text to uppercase in Dart |\n217\t| `lowercase` | Transform text to lowercase in Dart |\n218\t| `capitalize` | Capitalize in Dart |\n219\t\n220\t### Letter & Line Spacing\n221\t\n222\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n223\t|----------|---------|\n224\t| `tracking-tighter` | `letterSpacing: -0.8` |\n225\t| `tracking-tight` | `letterSpacing: -0.4` |\n226\t| `tracking-normal` | `letterSpacing: 0` |\n227\t| `tracking-wide` | `letterSpacing: 0.4` |\n228\t| `tracking-wider` | `letterSpacing: 0.8` |\n229\t| `tracking-widest` | `letterSpacing: 1.6` |\n230\t| `leading-none` | `height: 1.0` (in TextStyle) |\n231\t| `leading-tight` | `height: 1.25` |\n232\t| `leading-snug` | `height: 1.375` |\n233\t| `leading-normal` | `height: 1.5` |\n234\t| `leading-relaxed` | `height: 1.625` |\n235\t| `leading-loose` | `height: 2.0` |\n236\t\n237\t---\n238\t\n239\t## 7. Colors → Color Values\n240\t\n241\t### Format\n242\tTailwind colors map to `Color(0xAARRGGBB)` in Flutter.\n243\t\n244\t`text-{color}` → `TextStyle(color: Color(...))`\n245\t`bg-{color}` → Container/DecoratedBox color or widget background\n246\t`border-{color}` → `BorderSide(color: Color(...))`\n247\t\n248\t### Opacity Modifier\n249\t`bg-black/50` → `Color(0xFF000000).withOpacity(0.5)` or `Colors.black.withValues(alpha: 0.5)`\n250\t\n251\t### Slate (most used dark palette)\n252\t\n253\t| Tailwind | Hex | Color() |\n254\t|----------|-----|---------|\n255\t| `slate-50` | #f8fafc | `Color(0xFFF8FAFC)` |\n256\t| `slate-100` | #f1f5f9 | `Color(0xFFF1F5F9)` |\n257\t| `slate-200` | #e2e8f0 | `Color(0xFFE2E8F0)` |\n258\t| `slate-300` | #cbd5e1 | `Color(0xFFCBD5E1)` |\n259\t| `slate-400` | #94a3b8 | `Color(0xFF94A3B8)` |\n260\t| `slate-500` | #64748b | `Color(0xFF64748B)` |\n261\t| `slate-600` | #475569 | `Color(0xFF475569)` |\n262\t| `slate-700` | #334155 | `Color(0xFF334155)` |\n263\t| `slate-800` | #1e293b | `Color(0xFF1E293B)` |\n264\t| `slate-900` | #0f172a | `Color(0xFF0F172A)` |\n265\t| `slate-950` | #020617 | `Color(0xFF020617)` |\n266\t\n267\t### Amber (warm accent)\n268\t\n269\t| Tailwind | Hex | Color() |\n270\t|----------|-----|---------|\n271\t| `amber-50` | #fffbeb | `Color(0xFFFFFBEB)` |\n272\t| `amber-100` | #fef3c7 | `Color(0xFFFEF3C7)` |\n273\t| `amber-200` | #fde68a | `Color(0xFFFDE68A)` |\n274\t| `amber-300` | #fcd34d | `Color(0xFFFCD34D)` |\n275\t| `amber-400` | #fbbf24 | `Color(0xFFFBBF24)` |\n276\t| `amber-500` | #f59e0b | `Color(0xFFF59E0B)` |\n277\t| `amber-600` | #d97706 | `Color(0xFFD97706)` |\n278\t| `amber-700` | #b45309 | `Color(0xFFB45309)` |\n279\t| `amber-800` | #92400e | `Color(0xFF92400E)` |\n280\t| `amber-900` | #78350f | `Color(0xFF78350F)` |\n281\t| `amber-950` | #451a03 | `Color(0xFF451A03)` |\n282\t\n283\t### Common Utility Colors\n284\t\n285\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n286\t|----------|---------|\n287\t| `white` | `Colors.white` |\n288\t| `black` | `Colors.black` |\n289\t| `transparent` | `Colors.transparent` |\n290\t| `current` | `(inherit from parent)` |\n291\t\n292\t### Full Palette Families\n293\t\n294\tThe following families follow the same 50-950 scale: `red`, `orange`, `yellow`, `lime`, `green`, `emerald`, `teal`, `cyan`, `sky`, `blue`, `indigo`, `violet`, `purple`, `fuchsia`, `pink`, `rose`, `stone`, `neutral`, `zinc`, `gray`.\n295\t\n296\tFor the full hex values, reference: https://tailwindcss.com/docs/customizing-colors\n297\t\n298\t**Conversion strategy:** Extract the hex value from the Tailwind color reference and use `Color(0xFF{hex})`.\n299\t\n300\t---\n301\t\n302\t## 8. Borders → Border / BorderSide\n303\t\n304\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n305\t|----------|---------|\n306\t| `border` | `Border.all(width: 1)` |\n307\t| `border-0` | No border |\n308\t| `border-2` | `Border.all(width: 2)` |\n309\t| `border-4` | `Border.all(width: 4)` |\n310\t| `border-t` | `Border(top: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n311\t| `border-b` | `Border(bottom: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n312\t| `border-l` | `Border(left: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n313\t| `border-r` | `Border(right: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n314\t| `border-{color}` | `BorderSide(color: Color(...))` |\n315\t| `border-dashed` | Custom `Paint` with dashed style |\n316\t| `divide-y` | `ListView.separated` with `Divider()` |\n317\t| `divide-x` | `VerticalDivider()` between items |\n318\t\n319\t---\n320\t\n321\t## 9. Border Radius → BorderRadius\n322\t\n323\t| Tailwind | Pixels | Flutter |\n324\t|----------|--------|---------|\n325\t| `rounded-none` | 0 | `BorderRadius.zero` |\n326\t| `rounded-sm` | 2 | `BorderRadius.circular(2)` |\n327\t| `rounded` | 4 | `BorderRadius.circular(4)` |\n328\t| `rounded-md` | 6 | `BorderRadius.circular(6)` |\n329\t| `rounded-lg` | 8 | `BorderRadius.circular(8)` |\n330\t| `rounded-xl` | 12 | `BorderRadius.circular(12)` |\n331\t| `rounded-2xl` | 16 | `BorderRadius.circular(16)` |\n332\t| `rounded-3xl` | 24 | `BorderRadius.circular(24)` |\n333\t| `rounded-full` | 9999 | `BorderRadius.circular(9999)` → pill/circle |\n334\t| `rounded-t-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.vertical(top: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n335\t| `rounded-b-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.vertical(bottom: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n336\t| `rounded-l-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.horizontal(left: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n337\t| `rounded-r-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.horizontal(right: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n338\t\n339\t**Wrapping:** Use `ClipRRect(borderRadius: ...)` for clipping, or `DecoratedBox`/`Container` for decoration.\n340\t\n341\t---\n342\t\n343\t## 10. Shadows → BoxShadow\n344\t\n345\t| Tailwind | Flutter BoxShadow |\n346\t|----------|-------------------|\n347\t| `shadow-sm` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 2, offset: Offset(0, 1))` |\n348\t| `shadow` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 3, offset: Offset(0, 1)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0F000000), blurRadius: 2, offset: Offset(0, 1))` |\n349\t| `shadow-md` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 6, offset: Offset(0, 4)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0F000000), blurRadius: 4, offset: Offset(0, 2))` |\n350\t| `shadow-lg` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 15, offset: Offset(0, 10)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 6, offset: Offset(0, 4))` |\n351\t| `shadow-xl` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 25, offset: Offset(0, 20)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 10, offset: Offset(0, 8))` |\n352\t| `shadow-2xl` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x40000000), blurRadius: 50, offset: Offset(0, 25))` |\n353\t| `shadow-none` | No shadow |\n354\t\n355\t---\n356\t\n357\t## 11. Overflow → Clip / Scroll\n358\t\n359\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n360\t|----------|---------|\n361\t| `overflow-hidden` | `clipBehavior: Clip.hardEdge` or `ClipRect`/`ClipRRect` |\n362\t| `overflow-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView()` |\n363\t| `overflow-scroll` | `SingleChildScrollView()` |\n364\t| `overflow-visible` | Default (no clip) |\n365\t| `overflow-x-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView(scrollDirection: Axis.horizontal)` |\n366\t| `overflow-y-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView(scrollDirection: Axis.vertical)` |\n367\t\n368\t---\n369\t\n370\t## 12. Opacity → Opacity Widget\n371\t\n372\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n373\t|----------|---------|\n374\t| `opacity-0` | `Opacity(opacity: 0)` |\n375\t| `opacity-5` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.05)` |\n376\t| `opacity-10` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.1)` |\n377\t| `opacity-25` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.25)` |\n378\t| `opacity-50` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.5)` |\n379\t| `opacity-75` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.75)` |\n380\t| `opacity-100` | (no wrapper needed) |\n381\t\n382\t---\n383\t\n384\t## 13. Position → Positioned\n385\t\n386\t| Tailwind | Flutter (inside Stack) |\n387\t|----------|---------|\n388\t| `absolute inset-0` | `Positioned.fill()` |\n389\t| `absolute top-0 left-0` | `Positioned(top: 0, left: 0)` |\n390\t| `absolute bottom-0 right-0` | `Positioned(bottom: 0, right: 0)` |\n391\t| `absolute top-{n}` | `Positioned(top: {px})` |\n392\t| `absolute bottom-{n}` | `Positioned(bottom: {px})` |\n393\t| `z-{n}` | Child order in Stack (later = higher) |\n394\t| `z-10` | Order index 10 |\n395\t\n396\t---\n397\t\n398\t## 14. Effects → Flutter Equivalents\n399\t\n400\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n401\t|----------|---------|\n402\t| `backdrop-blur-sm` | `BackdropFilter(filter: ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 4, sigmaY: 4))` |\n403\t| `backdrop-blur` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 8, sigmaY: 8)` |\n404\t| `backdrop-blur-md` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 12, sigmaY: 12)` |\n405\t| `backdrop-blur-lg` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 16, sigmaY: 16)` |\n406\t| `backdrop-blur-xl` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 24, sigmaY: 24)` |\n407\t| `bg-gradient-to-r` | `LinearGradient(begin: Alignment.centerLeft, end: Alignment.centerRight)` |\n408\t| `bg-gradient-to-b` | `LinearGradient(begin: Alignment.topCenter, end: Alignment.bottomCenter)` |\n409\t| `from-{color}` | First color in gradient stops |\n410\t| `via-{color}` | Middle color in gradient stops |\n411\t| `to-{color}` | Last color in gradient stops |\n412\t\n413\t---\n414\t\n415\t## 15. Transitions & Animations\n416\t\n417\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n418\t|----------|---------|\n419\t| `transition-all` | `AnimatedContainer(duration: Duration(milliseconds: 150))` |\n420\t| `transition-colors` | `AnimatedDefaultTextStyle` or `AnimatedContainer` |\n421\t| `duration-75` | `Duration(milliseconds: 75)` |\n422\t| `duration-100` | `Duration(milliseconds: 100)` |\n423\t| `duration-150` | `Duration(milliseconds: 150)` |\n424\t| `duration-200` | `Duration(milliseconds: 200)` |\n425\t| `duration-300` | `Duration(milliseconds: 300)` |\n426\t| `duration-500` | `Duration(milliseconds: 500)` |\n427\t| `duration-700` | `Duration(milliseconds: 700)` |\n428\t| `duration-1000` | `Duration(milliseconds: 1000)` |\n429\t| `ease-linear` | `Curves.linear` |\n430\t| `ease-in` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n431\t| `ease-out` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n432\t| `ease-in-out` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n433\t\n434\t---\n435\t\n436\t## 16. Image Fit → BoxFit\n437\t\n438\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n439\t|----------|---------|\n440\t| `object-contain` | `BoxFit.contain` |\n441\t| `object-cover` | `BoxFit.cover` |\n442\t| `object-fill` | `BoxFit.fill` |\n443\t| `object-none` | `BoxFit.none` |\n444\t| `object-scale-down` | `BoxFit.scaleDown` |\n445\t\n446\t---\n447\t\n448\t## 17. Cursor & Interaction\n449\t\n450\t| Tailwind | Flutter |\n451\t|----------|---------|\n452\t| `cursor-pointer` | Wrap in `InkWell()` or `GestureDetector()` |\n453\t| `pointer-events-none` | `IgnorePointer()` |\n454\t| `select-none` | (default in Flutter) |\n455\t| `touch-manipulation` | (default in Flutter) |\n456\t\n457\t---\n458\t\n459\t## 18. Tailwind → Flutter Widget Decision Tree\n460\t\n461\tWhen converting a `<div>` with Tailwind classes:\n462\t\n463\t1. **Has `flex flex-col`?** → `Column()`\n464\t2. **Has `flex` or `flex flex-row`?** → `Row()`\n465\t3. **Has `grid`?** → `GridView()`\n466\t4. **Has `overflow-y-auto` or `overflow-auto`?** → `SingleChildScrollView()`\n467\t5. **Has `relative`?** → `Stack()` (its `absolute` children become `Positioned`)\n468\t6. **Has `bg-*` + `rounded-*` + `shadow-*`?** → `Container()` or `DecoratedBox()`\n469\t7. **Has only `p-*`?** → `Padding()`\n470\t8. **Has only `w-*` and/or `h-*`?** → `SizedBox()`\n471\t9. **Otherwise** → `Container()` or collapse into parent\n472\t\n473\tFor `<span>` / `<p>` / `<h1>-<h6>` with text classes → `Text()` with `TextStyle`\n474\t\n475\tFor `<button>` → Determine button type from styling:\n476\t- Has prominent background color → `FilledButton()` or `ElevatedButton()`\n477\t- Has border, no fill → `OutlinedButton()`\n478\t- Text only → `TextButton()`\n479\t- Icon only → `IconButton()`\n480\t\n481\tFor `<img>` → `CachedNetworkImage()` or `Image.asset()`\n482\t\n483\tFor `<svg>` → `Icon()` (Material) or `SvgPicture.string()`\n484\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d694d667-118c-44d3-9ad5-314421a0ee8d","uuid":"3df4a8bc-7a5e-475c-965a-69c407319c04","timestamp":"2026-05-18T23:46:21.088Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.converge/skills/stitch-flutter/references/tailwind-to-flutter.md","content":"# Tailwind CSS → Flutter Mapping\n\nComprehensive mapping of Tailwind utility classes to Flutter widget properties. The converter parses each Tailwind class and produces the exact Flutter equivalent.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Layout → Widget Type\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter Widget | Notes |\n|----------|---------------|-------|\n| `flex flex-col` | `Column()` | Vertical layout |\n| `flex` or `flex flex-row` | `Row()` | Horizontal layout (default axis) |\n| `inline-flex` | `Row(mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min)` | Inline row |\n| `grid grid-cols-{n}` | `GridView.count(crossAxisCount: n)` | Grid |\n| `block` | `SizedBox(width: double.infinity)` | Full width block |\n| `hidden` | `SizedBox.shrink()` or omit | Hidden element |\n| `relative` | `Stack()` (on parent) | Position context |\n| `absolute` | `Positioned()` | Absolute positioning inside Stack |\n| `fixed` | `Scaffold.bottomNavigationBar` or overlay | Fixed position |\n| `sticky` | `SliverAppBar(pinned: true)` | Sticky header |\n\n## 2. Flex Properties\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter | Notes |\n|----------|---------|-------|\n| `flex-1` | `Expanded(flex: 1)` | Fill remaining space |\n| `flex-auto` | `Expanded()` | Auto flex |\n| `flex-none` | (no wrapper) | Don't flex |\n| `flex-shrink-0` | (no wrapper) | Don't shrink |\n| `grow` | `Expanded()` | Grow to fill |\n| `flex-wrap` | `Wrap()` | Use Wrap instead of Row |\n| `flex-nowrap` | `Row()` | Default — no wrap |\n\n### Main Axis Alignment (Row → horizontal, Column → vertical)\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `justify-start` | `MainAxisAlignment.start` |\n| `justify-center` | `MainAxisAlignment.center` |\n| `justify-end` | `MainAxisAlignment.end` |\n| `justify-between` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceBetween` |\n| `justify-around` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceAround` |\n| `justify-evenly` | `MainAxisAlignment.spaceEvenly` |\n\n### Cross Axis Alignment\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `items-start` | `CrossAxisAlignment.start` |\n| `items-center` | `CrossAxisAlignment.center` |\n| `items-end` | `CrossAxisAlignment.end` |\n| `items-stretch` | `CrossAxisAlignment.stretch` |\n| `items-baseline` | `CrossAxisAlignment.baseline` |\n\n### Self Alignment\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `self-start` | `Align(alignment: Alignment.centerLeft)` |\n| `self-center` | `Center()` |\n| `self-end` | `Align(alignment: Alignment.centerRight)` |\n| `self-stretch` | `SizedBox(width: double.infinity)` |\n\n### Gap (spacing between children)\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `gap-0` | No spacing |\n| `gap-0.5` | 2px SizedBox between children |\n| `gap-1` | 4px |\n| `gap-1.5` | 6px |\n| `gap-2` | 8px |\n| `gap-2.5` | 10px |\n| `gap-3` | 12px |\n| `gap-4` | 16px |\n| `gap-5` | 20px |\n| `gap-6` | 24px |\n| `gap-8` | 32px |\n| `gap-10` | 40px |\n| `gap-12` | 48px |\n| `gap-x-{n}` | Horizontal gap only (Row) |\n| `gap-y-{n}` | Vertical gap only (Column) |\n| `space-x-{n}` | SizedBox(width: {n*4}px) between Row children |\n| `space-y-{n}` | SizedBox(height: {n*4}px) between Column children |\n\n**Implementation:** Insert `SizedBox(width/height: X)` between each child pair, or use Column/Row `spacing:` parameter (Flutter 3.27+).\n\n---\n\n## 3. Spacing Scale → Pixel Values\n\nAll spacing utilities (`p-`, `m-`, `gap-`, `w-`, `h-`, `inset-`, `top-`, etc.) use this scale:\n\n| Tailwind | Pixels | Tailwind | Pixels |\n|----------|--------|----------|--------|\n| `0` | 0 | `10` | 40 |\n| `px` | 1 | `11` | 44 |\n| `0.5` | 2 | `12` | 48 |\n| `1` | 4 | `14` | 56 |\n| `1.5` | 6 | `16` | 64 |\n| `2` | 8 | `20` | 80 |\n| `2.5` | 10 | `24` | 96 |\n| `3` | 12 | `28` | 112 |\n| `3.5` | 14 | `32` | 128 |\n| `4` | 16 | `36` | 144 |\n| `5` | 20 | `40` | 160 |\n| `6` | 24 | `44` | 176 |\n| `7` | 28 | `48` | 192 |\n| `8` | 32 | `52` | 208 |\n| `9` | 36 | `56` | 224 |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Padding → EdgeInsets\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `p-{n}` | `Padding(padding: EdgeInsets.all({px}))` |\n| `px-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: {px})` |\n| `py-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.symmetric(vertical: {px})` |\n| `pt-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(top: {px})` |\n| `pb-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(bottom: {px})` |\n| `pl-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(left: {px})` |\n| `pr-{n}` | `EdgeInsets.only(right: {px})` |\n| `ps-{n}` | `EdgeInsetsDirectional.only(start: {px})` |\n| `pe-{n}` | `EdgeInsetsDirectional.only(end: {px})` |\n\n**Combined:** `px-4 py-2` → `EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 16, vertical: 8)`\n\n**Wrapping:** Use `Padding()` widget wrapping the child.\n\n---\n\n## 5. Width & Height → SizedBox / Constraints\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `w-{n}` | `SizedBox(width: {px})` or `width: {px}` in Container |\n| `h-{n}` | `SizedBox(height: {px})` or `height: {px}` in Container |\n| `w-full` | `SizedBox(width: double.infinity)` |\n| `h-full` | `SizedBox(height: double.infinity)` |\n| `w-screen` | `MediaQuery.of(context).size.width` |\n| `h-screen` | `MediaQuery.of(context).size.height` |\n| `min-w-0` | `ConstrainedBox(constraints: BoxConstraints(minWidth: 0))` |\n| `min-h-screen` | `ConstrainedBox(constraints: BoxConstraints(minHeight: screenHeight))` |\n| `max-w-sm` | `ConstrainedBox(constraints: BoxConstraints(maxWidth: 384))` |\n| `max-w-md` | `maxWidth: 448` |\n| `max-w-lg` | `maxWidth: 512` |\n| `max-w-xl` | `maxWidth: 576` |\n| `max-w-screen-sm` | `maxWidth: 640` |\n| `size-{n}` | `SizedBox(width: {px}, height: {px})` |\n| `aspect-square` | `AspectRatio(aspectRatio: 1)` |\n| `aspect-video` | `AspectRatio(aspectRatio: 16/9)` |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Typography → TextStyle\n\n### Font Size\n\n| Tailwind | fontSize | lineHeight | Flutter TextTheme hint |\n|----------|----------|------------|----------------------|\n| `text-xs` | 12 | 16 | `labelSmall` |\n| `text-sm` | 14 | 20 | `bodySmall` / `labelLarge` |\n| `text-base` | 16 | 24 | `bodyLarge` |\n| `text-lg` | 18 | 28 | `titleMedium` |\n| `text-xl` | 20 | 28 | `titleLarge` |\n| `text-2xl` | 24 | 32 | `headlineSmall` |\n| `text-3xl` | 30 | 36 | `headlineMedium` |\n| `text-4xl` | 36 | 40 | `headlineLarge` |\n| `text-5xl` | 48 | 1.0 | `displaySmall` |\n| `text-6xl` | 60 | 1.0 | `displayMedium` |\n| `text-7xl` | 72 | 1.0 | `displayLarge` |\n\n### Font Weight\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `font-thin` | `FontWeight.w100` |\n| `font-extralight` | `FontWeight.w200` |\n| `font-light` | `FontWeight.w300` |\n| `font-normal` | `FontWeight.w400` |\n| `font-medium` | `FontWeight.w500` |\n| `font-semibold` | `FontWeight.w600` |\n| `font-bold` | `FontWeight.w700` |\n| `font-extrabold` | `FontWeight.w800` |\n| `font-black` | `FontWeight.w900` |\n\n### Text Alignment\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `text-left` | `TextAlign.left` |\n| `text-center` | `TextAlign.center` |\n| `text-right` | `TextAlign.right` |\n| `text-justify` | `TextAlign.justify` |\n\n### Text Overflow\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `truncate` | `overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis, maxLines: 1` |\n| `text-ellipsis` | `overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis` |\n| `text-clip` | `overflow: TextOverflow.clip` |\n| `line-clamp-{n}` | `maxLines: n, overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis` |\n\n### Text Decoration\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `underline` | `decoration: TextDecoration.underline` |\n| `line-through` | `decoration: TextDecoration.lineThrough` |\n| `no-underline` | `decoration: TextDecoration.none` |\n| `italic` | `fontStyle: FontStyle.italic` |\n| `not-italic` | `fontStyle: FontStyle.normal` |\n| `uppercase` | Transform text to uppercase in Dart |\n| `lowercase` | Transform text to lowercase in Dart |\n| `capitalize` | Capitalize in Dart |\n\n### Letter & Line Spacing\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `tracking-tighter` | `letterSpacing: -0.8` |\n| `tracking-tight` | `letterSpacing: -0.4` |\n| `tracking-normal` | `letterSpacing: 0` |\n| `tracking-wide` | `letterSpacing: 0.4` |\n| `tracking-wider` | `letterSpacing: 0.8` |\n| `tracking-widest` | `letterSpacing: 1.6` |\n| `leading-none` | `height: 1.0` (in TextStyle) |\n| `leading-tight` | `height: 1.25` |\n| `leading-snug` | `height: 1.375` |\n| `leading-normal` | `height: 1.5` |\n| `leading-relaxed` | `height: 1.625` |\n| `leading-loose` | `height: 2.0` |\n\n---\n\n## 7. Colors → Color Values\n\n### Format\nTailwind colors map to `Color(0xAARRGGBB)` in Flutter.\n\n`text-{color}` → `TextStyle(color: Color(...))`\n`bg-{color}` → Container/DecoratedBox color or widget background\n`border-{color}` → `BorderSide(color: Color(...))`\n\n### Opacity Modifier\n`bg-black/50` → `Color(0xFF000000).withOpacity(0.5)` or `Colors.black.withValues(alpha: 0.5)`\n\n### Slate (most used dark palette)\n\n| Tailwind | Hex | Color() |\n|----------|-----|---------|\n| `slate-50` | #f8fafc | `Color(0xFFF8FAFC)` |\n| `slate-100` | #f1f5f9 | `Color(0xFFF1F5F9)` |\n| `slate-200` | #e2e8f0 | `Color(0xFFE2E8F0)` |\n| `slate-300` | #cbd5e1 | `Color(0xFFCBD5E1)` |\n| `slate-400` | #94a3b8 | `Color(0xFF94A3B8)` |\n| `slate-500` | #64748b | `Color(0xFF64748B)` |\n| `slate-600` | #475569 | `Color(0xFF475569)` |\n| `slate-700` | #334155 | `Color(0xFF334155)` |\n| `slate-800` | #1e293b | `Color(0xFF1E293B)` |\n| `slate-900` | #0f172a | `Color(0xFF0F172A)` |\n| `slate-950` | #020617 | `Color(0xFF020617)` |\n\n### Amber (warm accent)\n\n| Tailwind | Hex | Color() |\n|----------|-----|---------|\n| `amber-50` | #fffbeb | `Color(0xFFFFFBEB)` |\n| `amber-100` | #fef3c7 | `Color(0xFFFEF3C7)` |\n| `amber-200` | #fde68a | `Color(0xFFFDE68A)` |\n| `amber-300` | #fcd34d | `Color(0xFFFCD34D)` |\n| `amber-400` | #fbbf24 | `Color(0xFFFBBF24)` |\n| `amber-500` | #f59e0b | `Color(0xFFF59E0B)` |\n| `amber-600` | #d97706 | `Color(0xFFD97706)` |\n| `amber-700` | #b45309 | `Color(0xFFB45309)` |\n| `amber-800` | #92400e | `Color(0xFF92400E)` |\n| `amber-900` | #78350f | `Color(0xFF78350F)` |\n| `amber-950` | #451a03 | `Color(0xFF451A03)` |\n\n### Common Utility Colors\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `white` | `Colors.white` |\n| `black` | `Colors.black` |\n| `transparent` | `Colors.transparent` |\n| `current` | `(inherit from parent)` |\n\n### Full Palette Families\n\nThe following families follow the same 50-950 scale: `red`, `orange`, `yellow`, `lime`, `green`, `emerald`, `teal`, `cyan`, `sky`, `blue`, `indigo`, `violet`, `purple`, `fuchsia`, `pink`, `rose`, `stone`, `neutral`, `zinc`, `gray`.\n\nFor the full hex values, reference: https://tailwindcss.com/docs/customizing-colors\n\n**Conversion strategy:** Extract the hex value from the Tailwind color reference and use `Color(0xFF{hex})`.\n\n---\n\n## 8. Borders → Border / BorderSide\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `border` | `Border.all(width: 1)` |\n| `border-0` | No border |\n| `border-2` | `Border.all(width: 2)` |\n| `border-4` | `Border.all(width: 4)` |\n| `border-t` | `Border(top: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n| `border-b` | `Border(bottom: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n| `border-l` | `Border(left: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n| `border-r` | `Border(right: BorderSide(width: 1))` |\n| `border-{color}` | `BorderSide(color: Color(...))` |\n| `border-dashed` | Custom `Paint` with dashed style |\n| `divide-y` | `ListView.separated` with `Divider()` |\n| `divide-x` | `VerticalDivider()` between items |\n\n---\n\n## 9. Border Radius → BorderRadius\n\n| Tailwind | Pixels | Flutter |\n|----------|--------|---------|\n| `rounded-none` | 0 | `BorderRadius.zero` |\n| `rounded-sm` | 2 | `BorderRadius.circular(2)` |\n| `rounded` | 4 | `BorderRadius.circular(4)` |\n| `rounded-md` | 6 | `BorderRadius.circular(6)` |\n| `rounded-lg` | 8 | `BorderRadius.circular(8)` |\n| `rounded-xl` | 12 | `BorderRadius.circular(12)` |\n| `rounded-2xl` | 16 | `BorderRadius.circular(16)` |\n| `rounded-3xl` | 24 | `BorderRadius.circular(24)` |\n| `rounded-full` | 9999 | `BorderRadius.circular(9999)` → pill/circle |\n| `rounded-t-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.vertical(top: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n| `rounded-b-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.vertical(bottom: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n| `rounded-l-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.horizontal(left: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n| `rounded-r-{size}` | | `BorderRadius.horizontal(right: Radius.circular({px}))` |\n\n**Wrapping:** Use `ClipRRect(borderRadius: ...)` for clipping, or `DecoratedBox`/`Container` for decoration.\n\n---\n\n## 10. Shadows → BoxShadow\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter BoxShadow |\n|----------|-------------------|\n| `shadow-sm` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 2, offset: Offset(0, 1))` |\n| `shadow` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 3, offset: Offset(0, 1)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0F000000), blurRadius: 2, offset: Offset(0, 1))` |\n| `shadow-md` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 6, offset: Offset(0, 4)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0F000000), blurRadius: 4, offset: Offset(0, 2))` |\n| `shadow-lg` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 15, offset: Offset(0, 10)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 6, offset: Offset(0, 4))` |\n| `shadow-xl` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x1A000000), blurRadius: 25, offset: Offset(0, 20)), BoxShadow(color: Color(0x0D000000), blurRadius: 10, offset: Offset(0, 8))` |\n| `shadow-2xl` | `BoxShadow(color: Color(0x40000000), blurRadius: 50, offset: Offset(0, 25))` |\n| `shadow-none` | No shadow |\n\n---\n\n## 11. Overflow → Clip / Scroll\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `overflow-hidden` | `clipBehavior: Clip.hardEdge` or `ClipRect`/`ClipRRect` |\n| `overflow-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView()` |\n| `overflow-scroll` | `SingleChildScrollView()` |\n| `overflow-visible` | Default (no clip) |\n| `overflow-x-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView(scrollDirection: Axis.horizontal)` |\n| `overflow-y-auto` | `SingleChildScrollView(scrollDirection: Axis.vertical)` |\n\n---\n\n## 12. Opacity → Opacity Widget\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `opacity-0` | `Opacity(opacity: 0)` |\n| `opacity-5` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.05)` |\n| `opacity-10` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.1)` |\n| `opacity-25` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.25)` |\n| `opacity-50` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.5)` |\n| `opacity-75` | `Opacity(opacity: 0.75)` |\n| `opacity-100` | (no wrapper needed) |\n\n---\n\n## 13. Position → Positioned\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter (inside Stack) |\n|----------|---------|\n| `absolute inset-0` | `Positioned.fill()` |\n| `absolute top-0 left-0` | `Positioned(top: 0, left: 0)` |\n| `absolute bottom-0 right-0` | `Positioned(bottom: 0, right: 0)` |\n| `absolute top-{n}` | `Positioned(top: {px})` |\n| `absolute bottom-{n}` | `Positioned(bottom: {px})` |\n| `z-{n}` | Child order in Stack (later = higher) |\n| `z-10` | Order index 10 |\n\n---\n\n## 14. Effects → Flutter Equivalents\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `backdrop-blur-sm` | `BackdropFilter(filter: ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 4, sigmaY: 4))` |\n| `backdrop-blur` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 8, sigmaY: 8)` |\n| `backdrop-blur-md` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 12, sigmaY: 12)` |\n| `backdrop-blur-lg` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 16, sigmaY: 16)` |\n| `backdrop-blur-xl` | `ImageFilter.blur(sigmaX: 24, sigmaY: 24)` |\n| `bg-gradient-to-r` | `LinearGradient(begin: Alignment.centerLeft, end: Alignment.centerRight)` |\n| `bg-gradient-to-b` | `LinearGradient(begin: Alignment.topCenter, end: Alignment.bottomCenter)` |\n| `from-{color}` | First color in gradient stops |\n| `via-{color}` | Middle color in gradient stops |\n| `to-{color}` | Last color in gradient stops |\n\n---\n\n## 15. Transitions & Animations\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `transition-all` | `AnimatedContainer(duration: Duration(milliseconds: 150))` |\n| `transition-colors` | `AnimatedDefaultTextStyle` or `AnimatedContainer` |\n| `duration-75` | `Duration(milliseconds: 75)` |\n| `duration-100` | `Duration(milliseconds: 100)` |\n| `duration-150` | `Duration(milliseconds: 150)` |\n| `duration-200` | `Duration(milliseconds: 200)` |\n| `duration-300` | `Duration(milliseconds: 300)` |\n| `duration-500` | `Duration(milliseconds: 500)` |\n| `duration-700` | `Duration(milliseconds: 700)` |\n| `duration-1000` | `Duration(milliseconds: 1000)` |\n| `ease-linear` | `Curves.linear` |\n| `ease-in` | `Curves.easeIn` |\n| `ease-out` | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| `ease-in-out` | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n\n---\n\n## 16. Image Fit → BoxFit\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `object-contain` | `BoxFit.contain` |\n| `object-cover` | `BoxFit.cover` |\n| `object-fill` | `BoxFit.fill` |\n| `object-none` | `BoxFit.none` |\n| `object-scale-down` | `BoxFit.scaleDown` |\n\n---\n\n## 17. Cursor & Interaction\n\n| Tailwind | Flutter |\n|----------|---------|\n| `cursor-pointer` | Wrap in `InkWell()` or `GestureDetector()` |\n| `pointer-events-none` | `IgnorePointer()` |\n| `select-none` | (default in Flutter) |\n| `touch-manipulation` | (default in Flutter) |\n\n---\n\n## 18. Tailwind → Flutter Widget Decision Tree\n\nWhen converting a `<div>` with Tailwind classes:\n\n1. **Has `flex flex-col`?** → `Column()`\n2. **Has `flex` or `flex flex-row`?** → `Row()`\n3. **Has `grid`?** → `GridView()`\n4. **Has `overflow-y-auto` or `overflow-auto`?** → `SingleChildScrollView()`\n5. **Has `relative`?** → `Stack()` (its `absolute` children become `Positioned`)\n6. **Has `bg-*` + `rounded-*` + `shadow-*`?** → `Container()` or `DecoratedBox()`\n7. **Has only `p-*`?** → `Padding()`\n8. **Has only `w-*` and/or `h-*`?** → `SizedBox()`\n9. **Otherwise** → `Container()` or collapse into parent\n\nFor `<span>` / `<p>` / `<h1>-<h6>` with text classes → `Text()` with `TextStyle`\n\nFor `<button>` → Determine button type from styling:\n- Has prominent background color → `FilledButton()` or `ElevatedButton()`\n- Has border, no fill → `OutlinedButton()`\n- Text only → `TextButton()`\n- Icon only → `IconButton()`\n\nFor `<img>` → `CachedNetworkImage()` or `Image.asset()`\n\nFor `<svg>` → `Icon()` (Material) or `SvgPicture.string()`\n","numLines":484,"startLine":1,"totalLines":484}}}
