The screen structure includes a lavender app bar with back navigation, a main content area with a current cycle card showing the day count and progress, a cycle history section with a list of past cycles, and a floating action button to add new entries, with a bottom sheet for logging cycles.

For the scaffold, I'm setting up a lavender tint background with an app bar in lavender primary color containing a back button and title. The body uses a ListView with padding, and there's a floating action button positioned in lavender with a white plus icon. The main cycle card displays a day badge, the current day count, next period date, and a fertile window section.

The cycle history displays a header followed by cards for each past cycle. For the bottom sheet, I'm implementing a modal with a handle bar, title, date and cycle length fields, notes input, an irregular cycle toggle, and action buttons for cancel and save.

